# <a name="sensitive-information-type-entity-definitions"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-104">Определения типов конфиденциальной информации</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-104">Sensitive information type entity definitions</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-105">Тип конфиденциальной информации определяется шаблоном, который можно идентифицировать регулярным выражением или функцией.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-105">A sensitive information type is defined by a pattern that can be identified by a regular expression or a function.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-106">Кроме того, для идентификации типа конфиденциальной информации могут использоваться подкрепляющие доказательства, такие как ключевые слова и контрольные суммы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-106">In addition, corroborative evidence such as keywords and checksums can be used to identify a sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-107">Уровень вероятности и расположение слов и знаков также используются в процессе оценки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-107">Confidence level and proximity are also used in the evaluation process.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-108">Для типов конфиденциальной информации требуется одна из этих подписок:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-108">Sensitive information types require one of these subscriptions:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-109">Microsoft 365 E3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-109">Microsoft 365 E3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-110">Microsoft 365 E5</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-110">Microsoft 365 E5</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-111">Типы конфиденциальной информации используются в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-111">Sensitive information types are used in:</span></span>

- [<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-112">Политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-112">Data loss prevention policies</span></span>](data-loss-prevention-policies.md) 
- [<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-113">Метки конфиденциальности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-113">Sensitivity labels</span></span>](sensitivity-labels.md)
- [<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-114">Метки хранения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-114">Retention labels</span></span>](retention.md)
- [<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-115">Соответствие требованиям к обмену данными</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-115">Communication compliance</span></span>](communication-compliance.md)
- [<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-116">Политики автоматической маркировки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-116">Auto-labelling policies</span></span>](apply-sensitivity-label-automatically.md#how-to-configure-auto-labeling-for-office-apps)

## <a name="aba-routing-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-117">Номер маршрутки ABA</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-117">ABA routing number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-118">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-118">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-119">девять цифр, которые могут быть в форматированном или неформатированном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-119">nine digits which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-120">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-120">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-121">Формат:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-121">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-122">четыре цифры, начиная с 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7 или 8</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-122">four digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-123">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-123">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-124">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-124">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-125">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-125">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-126">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-126">a digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-127">Неформатированные: девять последовательных цифр, начиная с 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7 или 8</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-127">Unformatted: nine consecutive digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span> 

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-128">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-128">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-129">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-129">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-130">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-130">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-131">Политика имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-131">A policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-132">функция Func_aba_routing находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-132">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-133">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ABA_Routing.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-133">A keyword from Keyword_ABA_Routing is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-134">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-134">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-135">функция Func_aba_routing находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-135">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- ABA Routing Number -->
    <Entity id="cb353f78-2b72-4c3c-8827-92ebe4f69fdf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ABA_Routing" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_aba_routing"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-137">Keyword_aba_routing</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-137">Keyword_aba_routing</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-138">aba number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-138">aba number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-140">aba</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-140">aba</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-141">abarouting #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-141">abarouting#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-142">abaroutingnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-142">abaroutingnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-143">americanbankassociationrouting #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-143">americanbankassociationrouting#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-144">americanbankassociationroutingnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-144">americanbankassociationroutingnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-145">bankrouting #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-145">bankrouting#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-146">bankroutingnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-146">bankroutingnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-147">routing #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-147">routing #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-148">no routing</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-148">routing no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-149">номер маршрутной маршрутки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-149">routing number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-150">routing transit number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-150">routing transit number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-151">routing #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-151">routing#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-152">RTN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-152">RTN</span></span>


## <a name="argentina-national-identity-dni-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-153">Номер удостоверения личности для Аргентины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-153">Argentina national identity (DNI) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-154">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-154">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-155">Восемь цифр с периодами или без них</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-155">Eight digits with or without periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-156">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-156">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-157">Восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-157">Eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-158">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-158">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-159">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-159">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-160">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-160">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-161">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-161">an optional period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-162">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-162">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-163">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-163">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-164">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-164">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-165">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-165">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-166">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-166">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-167">регулярное выражение Regex_argentina_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-167">The regular expression Regex_argentina_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-168">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_argentina_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-168">A keyword from Keyword_argentina_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Argentina National Identity (DNI) Number -->
<Entity id="eefbb00e-8282-433c-8620-8f1da3bffdb2" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_argentina_national_id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_argentina_national_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-174">dni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-174">dni</span></span>

## <a name="australia-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-180">Номер банковского счета для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-180">Australia bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-181">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-181">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-182">от шести до десяти цифр с номером филиала банковского состояния или без него</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-182">six to ten digits with or without a bank state branch number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-183">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-183">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-184">Номер учетной записи — от шести до десяти цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-184">Account number is six to ten digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-185">Номер филиала государственного банка Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-185">Australia bank state branch number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-186">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-186">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-187">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-187">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-188">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-188">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-189">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-189">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-190">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-190">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-191">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-191">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-192">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-192">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-193">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-193">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-194">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-194">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-195">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-195">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-196">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-196">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-197">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-197">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-198">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-198">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="74a54de9-2a30-4aa0-a8aa-3d9327fc07c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb" />
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
  </Pattern>
 </Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-business-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-214">Номер компании для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-214">Australia business number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-215">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-215">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-216">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-216">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-217">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-217">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-218">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-218">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-219">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-219">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-220">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-220">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-221">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-221">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-222">11 цифр с необязательными делегаторами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-222">11 digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-223">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-223">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-224">11 цифр с необязательными делегаторами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-224">11 digits with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-225">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-225">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-226">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-226">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-227">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-227">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-228">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-228">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-229">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-229">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-230">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-230">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-231">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-231">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-232">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-232">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-233">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-233">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-234">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-234">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-235">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-235">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-236">Функция Func_australian_business_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-236">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-237">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_australian_business_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-237">A keyword from Keywords_australian_business_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-238">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-238">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-239">Функция Func_australian_business_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-239">The function Func_australian_business_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Business Number -->
      <Entity id="76e83b3b-01ee-4530-aced-e667a6609f49" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_business_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-250">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-250">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-251">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-251">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-252">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-252">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-253">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-253">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-254">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-254">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-255">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-255">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-256">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-256">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-257">девять цифр с делетерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-257">nine digits with delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-258">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-258">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-259">девять цифр с делегаторами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-259">nine digits with delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-260">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-260">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-261">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-261">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-262">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-262">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-263">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-263">a space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-264">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-264">three digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-265">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-265">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-266">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-266">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-267">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-267">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-268">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-268">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-269">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-269">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-270">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Australian_Company_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-270">A keyword from Keyword_Australian_Company_Number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-271">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-271">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-272">Функция Func_Australian_Company_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-272">The function Func_Australian_Company_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Australia Company Number -->
      <Entity id="b1fba4f7-7b3e-4bb9-8f9a-9366df604dbb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Australian_Company_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_australia_company_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-274">Keyword_australia_company_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-274">Keyword_australia_company_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-275">can</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-275">acn</span></span>

## <a name="australia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-282">Номер водительского удостоверения для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-282">Australia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-283">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-283">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-284">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-284">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-285">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-285">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-286">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-286">nine letters and digits:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-287">две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-287">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-288">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-288">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-289">пять цифр или букв (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-289">five digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-290">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-290">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-291">от одной до двух необязательных букв (без чувствительность к буквам);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-291">one to two optional letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-292">от четырех до девяти цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-292">four to nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-293">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-293">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-294">девять цифр или букв (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-294">nine digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-295">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-295">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-296">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-296">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-297">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-297">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-298">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-298">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-299">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-299">The regular expression Regex_australia_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-300">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-300">A keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-301">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-301">No keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Drivers License Number -->
<Entity id="1cbbc8f5-9216-4392-9eb5-5ac2298d1356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-302">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-302">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="australia-medical-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-401">Номер медицинской учетной записи для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-401">Australia medical account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-402">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-402">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-403">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-403">10-11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-404">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-404">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-405">10–11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-405">10-11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-406">первая цифра находится в диапазоне от 2 до 6</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-406">first digit is in the range 2-6</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-407">девятая цифра является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-407">ninth digit is a check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-408">десятая цифра — это цифра проблемы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-408">tenth digit is the issue digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-409">одиннадцатая цифра (необязательно) — это отдельный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-409">eleventh digit (optional) is the individual number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-410">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-410">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-411">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-411">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-412">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-412">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-413">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-413">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-414">функция Func_australian_medical_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-414">The function Func_australian_medical_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-415">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-415">A keyword from Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-416">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-416">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
  <!-- Australia Medical Account Number -->
<Entity id="104a99a0-3d3b-4542-a40d-ab0b9e1efe63" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_medical_account_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number"/>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-428">Номер паспорта гражданина Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-428">Australia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-429">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-429">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-430">Буква, за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-430">A letter followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-431">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-431">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-432">Буква (без учета регистра), за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-432">A letter (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-433">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-433">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-434">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-434">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-435">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-435">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-436">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-436">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-437">регулярное выражение Regex_australia_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-437">The regular expression Regex_australia_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-438">Находится ключевое слово Keyword_passport или Keyword_australia_passport_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-438">A keyword from Keyword_passport or Keyword_australia_passport_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Passport Number -->
<Entity id="29869db6-602d-4853-ab93-3484f905df50" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_passport_number" />
        </Any>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>   
```

## <a name="australia-tax-file-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-472">Номер налогового файла для Австралии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-472">Australia tax file number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-473">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-473">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-474">от восьми до девяти цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-474">eight to nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-475">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-475">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-476">От восьми до девяти цифр, как правило, представлены пробелы следующим образом:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-476">eight to nine digits typically presented with spaces as follows:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-477">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-477">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-478">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-478">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-479">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-479">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-480">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-480">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-481">две-три цифры, где последняя цифра является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-481">two to three digits where the last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-482">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-482">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-483">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-483">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-484">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-484">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-485">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-485">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-486">функция Func_australian_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-486">The function Func_australian_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-487">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number или Keyword_number_exclusions не найдено;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-487">No keyword from Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number or Keyword_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-488">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-488">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
   <!-- Australia Tax File Number -->
    <Entity id="e29bc95f-ff70-4a37-aa01-04d17360a4c5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_tax_file_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-500">Номер водительского удостоверения для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-500">Austria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-501">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-501">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-502">восемь цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-502">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-503">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-503">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-504">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-504">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-505">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-505">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-506">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-506">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-507">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-507">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-508">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-508">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-509">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-509">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-510">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-510">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="682f18ce-44eb-482b-8198-2bcb96a0761e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-637">Удостоверение личности для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-637">Austria identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-638">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-638">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-639">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-639">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-640">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-640">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-641">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-641">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-642">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-642">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-643">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-643">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-644">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-644">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-645">24-значное сочетание букв, цифр и специальных символов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-645">A 24-character combination of letters, digits, and special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-646">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-646">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-647">24 символа:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-647">24 characters:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-648">22 буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), цифры, косые черты, косые черты или знаки плюса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-648">22 letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, or plus signs</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-649">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), цифры, косые черты, косые черты, знаки плюс или знаки равного знака</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-649">two letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, plus signs, or equal signs</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-650">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-650">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-651">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-651">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-652">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-652">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-653">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-653">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-654">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-654">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-655">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-655">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
   
```xml
      <!-- Austria Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="5ec06c3b-007e-4820-8343-7ff73b889735" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-656">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-656">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-657">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-657">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-658">identity number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-658">identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-659">national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-659">national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-660">personalausweis repubich österreich</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-660">personalausweis republik österreich</span></span>

## <a name="austria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-661">Номер паспорта гражданина Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-661">Austria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-662">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-662">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-663">Одна буква, за которой следует необязательное пространство и семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-663">One letter followed by an optional space and seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-664">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-664">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-665">Сочетание одной буквы, семи цифр и одного пробела:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-665">A combination of one letter, seven digits, and one space:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-666">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-666">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-667">одно пространство (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-667">one space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-668">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-668">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-669">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-669">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-670">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-670">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-671">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-671">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-672">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-672">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-673">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-673">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-674">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-674">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-675">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-675">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-676">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-676">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-677">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-677">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-678">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-678">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1c96ae4e-303b-447d-86c7-77113ac266bf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-social-security-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-699">Номер социального обеспечения для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-699">Austria social security number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-700">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-700">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-701">10 цифр в указанном формате</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-701">10 digits in the specified format</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-702">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-702">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-703">10 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-703">10 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-704">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-704">three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-705">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-705">one check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-706">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММАЙ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-706">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-707">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-707">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-708">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-708">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-709">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-709">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-710">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, расположенного в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-710">A DLP policy is has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-711">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-711">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-712">находится ключевое слово  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` из.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-712">a keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-713">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-713">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-714">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-714">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Social Security Number -->
      <Entity id="6896a906-86c9-4d19-a2da-6e43ccd19b7b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-734">sozialesicherheitkein #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-734">sozialesicherheitkein#</span></span>

## <a name="austria-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-740">Идентификационный номер налога для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-740">Austria tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-741">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-741">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-742">девять цифр с необязательным дефишем и косой чертой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-742">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-743">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-743">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-744">девять цифр с необязательным дефишем и косой чертой:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-744">nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-745">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-745">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-746">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-746">a hyphen (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-747">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-747">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-748">косая черта (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-748">a forward slash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-749">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-749">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-750">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-750">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-751">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-751">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-752">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-752">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-753">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-753">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-754">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-754">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-755">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-755">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-756">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-756">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-757">Функция находит  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-757">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Austria Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="4fd58d22-af28-4451-b18a-6f722430a56d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-758">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-758">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-759">Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-759">Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-760">österreich</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-760">österreich</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-761">st.nr.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-761">st.nr.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-762">steuernummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-762">steuernummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-763">tax id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-763">tax id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-764">tax identification no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-764">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-765">налоговый идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-765">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-766">tax no #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-766">tax no#</span></span>
