## <a name="austria-value-added-tax"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-780">Налог на добавленную стоимость для Австрия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-780">Austria value added tax</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-781">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-781">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-782">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-782">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-783">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-783">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-784">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-784">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-785">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-785">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-786">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-786">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-787">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-787">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-788">11-символьный буквонумерный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-788">11-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-789">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-789">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-790">11-символьный буквонумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-790">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-791">A или a</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-791">A or a</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-792">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-792">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-793">Дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-793">Optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-794">U или u</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-794">U or u</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-795">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-795">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-796">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-796">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-797">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-797">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-798">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-798">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-799">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-799">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-800">одна или две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-800">one or two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-801">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-801">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-802">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-802">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-803">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-803">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-804">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-804">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-805">Функция Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-805">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-806">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-806">A keyword from Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-807">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-807">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-808">Функция Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-808">The function Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Austria Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="b6a3eda2-c56c-4b69-a5f7-dca34db00f48" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_Austria_Value_Added_Tax" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-809">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-809">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_austria_value_added_tax"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-810">Keyword_austria_value_added_tax</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-810">Keyword_austria_value_added_tax</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-811">номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-811">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-812">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-812">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-813">номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-813">austrian vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-814">vat no.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-814">vat no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-815">vatno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-815">vatno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-816">номер налога на добавленную стоимость</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-816">value added tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-817">vat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-817">austrian vat</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-818">mwst</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-818">mwst</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-819">umsatzsteuernummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-819">umsatzsteuernummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-820">mwstnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-820">mwstnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-821">ust.-identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-821">ust.-identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-822">umsatzsteuer-identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-822">umsatzsteuer-identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-823">идентификационный номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-823">vat identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-824">atu number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-824">atu number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-825">UID-номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-825">uid number</span></span>


## <a name="azure-documentdb-auth-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-826">Ключ проверки auth Azure DocumentDB</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-826">Azure DocumentDB auth key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-827">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-827">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-828">Строка DocumentDb, за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в шаблоне ниже.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-828">The string "DocumentDb" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-829">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-829">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-830">Строка DocumentDb</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-830">The string "DocumentDb"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-831">Любое сочетание от 3 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-831">Any combination of between 3-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-832">Больше символа (>), знака равного (=), кавычка (") или апостроф (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-832">A greater than symbol (>), an equal sign (=), a quotation mark ("), or an apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-833">Любое сочетание 86 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, косой черты (/) или знака плюса (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-833">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-834">Два знака равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-834">Two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-835">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-835">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-836">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-836">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-837">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-837">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-838">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-838">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-839">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-839">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-840">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords **не находит** содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-840">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Azure Document DB Auth Key -->
<Entity id="0f587d92-eb28-44a9-bd1c-90f2892b47aa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
          </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-841">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-841">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_commonexamplekeywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-842">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-842">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-843">(Обратите внимание, что технически этот тип конфиденциальной информации идентифицирует эти ключевые слова с помощью регулярного выражения, а не списка ключевых слов.)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-843">(Note that technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-844">contoso</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-844">contoso</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-845">fabrikam</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-845">fabrikam</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-846">northwind</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-846">northwind</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-847">песочница</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-847">sandbox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-848">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-848">onebox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-849">localhost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-849">localhost</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-850">127.0.0.1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-850">127.0.0.1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-851">testacs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-851">testacs.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-852">com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-852">com</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-853">s-int.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-853">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-854">net</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-854">net</span></span>

## <a name="azure-iaas-database-connection-string-and-azure-sql-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-855">Строка подключения к базе данных Azure IAAS и строка подключения Azure SQL Azure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-855">Azure IAAS database connection string and Azure SQL connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-856">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-856">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-857">Строка "Сервер", "сервер" или "источник данных", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне, включая строку "cloudapp.azure".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-857">The string "Server", "server", or "data source" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-858">com или cloudapp.azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-858">com" or "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-859">net или database.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-859">net" or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-860">net и строку "Password", "password" или "pwd".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-860">net", and the string "Password" or "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-861">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-861">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-862">строка "Сервер", "сервер" или "источник данных"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-862">the string "Server", "server", or "data source"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-863">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-863">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-864">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-864">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-865">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-865">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-866">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-866">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-867">Строка "cloudapp.azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-867">The string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-868">com, "cloudapp.azure.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-868">com", "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-869">net или database.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-869">net", or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-870">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-870">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-871">любое сочетание от 1 до 300 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-871">any combination of between 1-300 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-872">строка "Password", "password" или "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-872">the string "Password", "password", or "pwd"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-873">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-873">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-874">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-874">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-875">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-875">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-876">один или несколько символов, которые не являются пустяковой (;), кавычка (") или апостроф (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-876">one or more characters that is not a semicolon (;), quotation mark ("), or apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-877">точка с зачетом (;), кавычка (") или апостроф (')</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-877">a semicolon (;), quotation mark ("), or apostrophe (')</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-878">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-878">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-879">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-879">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-880">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-880">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-881">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-881">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-882">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-882">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-883">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords **не находит** содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-883">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure IAAS Database Connection String and Azure SQL Connection String-->
<Entity id="ce1a126d-186f-4700-8c0c-486157b953fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-iot-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-898">Строка подключения Azure IoT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-898">Azure IoT connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-899">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-899">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-900">Строка HostName, за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне, включая строки "azure-devices".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-900">The string "HostName" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-901">net" и "SharedAccessKey".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-901">net" and "SharedAccessKey".</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-904">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-904">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-905">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-905">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-906">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-906">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-907">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-907">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-908">строка "azure-devices.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-908">the string "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-909">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-909">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-910">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-910">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-911">строка "SharedAccessKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-911">the string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-912">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-912">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-913">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-913">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-914">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-914">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-915">любое сочетание 43 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, косой черты (/) или знака плюса (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-915">any combination of 43 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-916">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-916">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-917">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-917">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-918">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-918">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-919">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-919">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-920">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-920">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-921">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-921">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-922">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords **не находит** содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-922">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-965">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-965">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-966">Строка redis.cache.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-966">The string "redis.cache.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-967">net, за которыми следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенной ниже схеме, включая строку "password" или "pwd".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-967">net" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-968">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-968">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-969">строка redis.cache.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-969">the string "redis.cache.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-970">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-970">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-971">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-971">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-972">строка "password" или "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-972">the string "password" or "pwd"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-973">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-973">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-974">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-974">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-975">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-975">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-976">любое сочетание 43 символов, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрами, косой чертой (/) или знаком плюса (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-976">any combination of 43 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-977">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-977">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-978">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-978">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-979">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-979">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-980">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-980">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-981">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-981">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-982">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-982">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-983">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords **не находит** содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-983">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Redis Cache Connection String-->
<Entity id="095a7e6c-efd8-46d5-af7b-5298d53a49fc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-984">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-984">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_common_example_keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-985">CEP_common_example_keywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-985">CEP_common_example_keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-991">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-991">onebox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-992">localhost</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-992">localhost</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-996">s-int.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-996">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-997">net</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-997">net</span></span>

## <a name="azure-sas"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-998">Azure SAS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-998">Azure SAS</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-999">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-999">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1000">Строка "sig", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенной ниже схеме.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1000">The string "sig" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1001">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1001">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1002">строка "sig"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1002">the string "sig"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1003">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1003">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1004">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1004">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1005">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1005">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1006">любое сочетание между 43–53 символами, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрами или знаком процента (%)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1006">any combination of between 43-53 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, or the percent sign (%)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1007">строка "%3d"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1007">the string "%3d"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1008">любой символ, который не является буквой нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрой или знаком процента (%)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1008">any character that is not a lower- or uppercase letter, digit, or percent sign (%)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1009">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1009">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1010">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1010">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1011">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1011">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1012">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1012">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1013">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureSAS находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1013">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureSAS finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure SAS-->
<Entity id="4d235014-e564-47f4-a6fb-6ebb4a826834" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureSAS" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-service-bus-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1014">Строка подключения к шине обслуживания Azure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1014">Azure service bus connection string</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1016">Строка "EndPoint", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенной ниже схеме, включая строки servicebus.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1016">The string "EndPoint" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "servicebus.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1017">net" и "SharedAccesKey".</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1017">net" and "SharedAccesKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1018">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1018">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1019">строка "EndPoint"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1019">the string "EndPoint"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1020">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1020">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1021">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1021">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1022">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1022">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1023">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1023">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1024">строка "servicebus.windows.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1024">the string "servicebus.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1025">net"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1025">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1026">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1026">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1027">строка "SharedAccessKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1027">the string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1028">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1028">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1029">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1029">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1030">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1030">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1031">любое сочетание 43 символов, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрами, косой чертой (/) или знаком плюса (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1031">any combination of 43 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1032">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1032">an equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1033">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1033">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1034">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1034">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1035">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1035">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1036">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1036">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1037">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1037">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>

```xml
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1053">Ключ учетной записи хранения Azure</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1053">Azure storage account key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1054">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1054">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1055">Строка "DefaultEndpointsProtocol", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в приведенной ниже схеме, включая строку AccountKey.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1055">The string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "AccountKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1056">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1056">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1057">строка "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1057">the string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1058">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1058">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1059">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1059">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1060">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1060">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1061">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1061">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1062">строка AccountKey</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1062">the string "AccountKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1063">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1063">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1064">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1064">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1065">от нуля до двух символов из белого пространства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1065">zero to two whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1066">любое сочетание 86 символов, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрами, косой чертой (/) или знаком плюса (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1066">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1067">два знака равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1067">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1068">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1068">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1069">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1069">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1070">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1070">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1071">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1071">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1072">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1072">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1073">Регулярное выражение CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter **не находит** содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1073">The regular expression CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1074">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords **не находит** содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1074">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key-->
<Entity id="c7bc98e8-551a-4c35-a92d-d2c8cda714a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key-generic"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1092">Ключ учетной записи хранилища Azure (универсальный)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1092">Azure Storage account key (generic)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1093">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1093">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1094">Любое сочетание 86 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, косой черты (/) или знака плюса (+), предшествующего или за которым следуют символы, описанные в приведенном ниже шаблоне.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1094">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+), preceded or followed by the characters outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1095">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1095">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1096">от нуля до одного из символов больше чем (>), апострофа ('), знака равного (=), кавычка (") или знака номера (#)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1096">zero to one of the greater than symbol (>), apostrophe ('), equal sign (=), quotation mark ("), or number sign (#)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1097">любое сочетание 86 символов, которые являются буквами нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифрами, косой чертой (/) или знаком плюса (+)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1097">any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1098">два знака равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1098">two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1099">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1099">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1100">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1100">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1101">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1101">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1102">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1102">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1103">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1103">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key (Generic)-->
<Entity id="7ff41bd0-5419-4523-91d6-383b3a37f084" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
## <a name="belgium-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1104">Номер водительского удостоверения для Бельгии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1104">Belgium driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1105">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1105">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1106">десять цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1106">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1107">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1107">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1108">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1108">ten digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1109">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1109">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1110">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1110">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1111">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1111">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1112">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1112">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1113">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1113">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1114">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1114">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Belgium Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d89fd329-9324-433c-b687-2c37bd5166f3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-national-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1247">Национальный номер для Бельгии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1247">Belgium national number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1248">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1248">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1249">11 цифр, а также необязательные делегаторы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1249">11 digits plus optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1250">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1250">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1251">11 цифр, а также разделители:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1251">11 digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1252">шесть цифр и два необязательных периода в формате YY. MM.DD для даты рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1252">six digits and two optional periods in the format YY.MM.DD for date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1253">Необязательный пунктир из точки, тире, пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1253">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1254">три последовательной цифры (нечетные для самцов, даже для самок)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1254">three sequential digits (odd for males, even for females)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1255">Необязательный пунктир из точки, тире, пробела</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1255">An optional delimiter from dot, dash, space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1256">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1256">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1257">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1257">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1258">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1258">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1259">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1259">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1260">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1260">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1261">функция Func_belgium_national_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1261">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1262">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_belgium_national_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1262">A keyword from Keyword_belgium_national_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1263">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1263">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1264">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1264">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1265">функция Func_belgium_national_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1265">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1266">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1266">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Belgium National Number -->
       <Entity id="fb969c9e-0fd1-4b18-8091-a2123c5e6a54" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1325">Номер паспорта гражданина Бельгии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1325">Belgium passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1326">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1326">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1327">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1327">two letters followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1328">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1328">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1329">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1329">two letters and followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1330">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1330">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1331">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1331">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1332">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1332">Definition</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1333">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1333">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1334">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1334">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1335">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1335">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1336">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date2` находит дату в формате ДД ММ YY или ключевое слово из `Keywords_eu_passport_date` или `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` найдено</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1336">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date2` finds date in the format DD MM YY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1337">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1337">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1338">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1338">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1339">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1339">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d7b1315b-21ca-4774-a32a-596010ff78fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date2" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="belgium-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1363">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость в Бельгии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1363">Belgium value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1364">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1364">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1365">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1365">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1366">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1366">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1367">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1367">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1368">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1368">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1369">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1369">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1370">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1370">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1371">12-символьный буквонумерный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1371">12-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1372">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1372">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1373">12-символьный буквонумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1373">12-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1374">буква B или b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1374">a letter B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1375">буква E или e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1375">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1376">цифра 0</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1376">a digit 0</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1377">цифра от 1 до 9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1377">a digit from 1 to 9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1378">необязательная точка, дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1378">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1379">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1379">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1380">необязательная точка, дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1380">an optional dot or Hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1381">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1381">four digits</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1382">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1382">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1383">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1383">Yes</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1384">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1384">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1385">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1385">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1386">Функция Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1386">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1387">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1387">A keyword from Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1388">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1388">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1389">Функция Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1389">The function Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Belgium Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="85b5b3c3-f2de-4ae8-ac46-fd3cb38bf9ed" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

## <a name="brazil-cpf-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1401">Номер CPF для Бразилии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1401">Brazil CPF number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1402">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1402">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1403">11 цифр, которые включают проверочную цифру и могут быть форматированными или неформатированными.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1403">11 digits that include a check digit and can be formatted or unformatted</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1404">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1404">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1405">Формат:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1405">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1406">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1406">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1407">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1407">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1408">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1408">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1409">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1409">a period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1410">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1410">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1411">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1411">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1412">две цифры, которые являются провероными цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1412">two digits which are check digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1413">Неформатированные:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1413">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1414">11 цифр, где две последние цифры — проверочные.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1414">11 digits where the last two digits are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1415">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1415">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1416">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1416">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1417">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1417">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1418">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1418">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1419">функция Func_brazil_cpf находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1419">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1420">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_brazil_cpf;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1420">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cpf is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1421">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1421">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1422">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1422">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1423">функция Func_brazil_cpf находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1423">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1424">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1424">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil CPF Number -->
<Entity id="78e09124-f2c3-4656-b32a-c1a132cd2711" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1432">Imposto</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1432">Imposto</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1433">Identificação</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1433">Identificação</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1434">Inscrição</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1434">Inscrição</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1435">Receita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1435">Receita</span></span> 

   
## <a name="brazil-legal-entity-number-cnpj"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1436">Номер юридического лица для Бразилии (CNPJ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1436">Brazil legal entity number (CNPJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1437">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1437">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1438">14 цифр, которые включают регистрационный номер, номер филиала и проверочные цифры, а также разделители.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1438">14 digits that include a registration number, branch number, and check digits, plus delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1439">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1439">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1440">14 цифр, а также разделители:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1440">14 digits, plus delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1441">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1441">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1442">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1442">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1443">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1443">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1444">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1444">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1445">три цифры (эти первые восемь цифр являются регистрационным номером)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1445">three digits (these first eight digits are the registration number)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1446">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1446">a forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1447">четырехзначный номер филиала</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1447">four-digit branch number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1448">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1448">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1449">две цифры, которые являются провероными цифрами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1449">two digits which are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1450">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1450">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1451">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1451">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1452">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1452">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1453">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1453">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1454">функция Func_brazil_cnpj находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1454">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1455">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_brazil_cnpj;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1455">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cnpj is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1456">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1456">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1457">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1457">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1458">функция Func_brazil_cnpj находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1458">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1459">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1459">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil Legal Entity Number (CNPJ) -->
<Entity id="9b58b5cd-5e90-4df6-b34f-1ebcc88ceae4" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
