## <a name="brazil-national-identification-card-rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1481">Национальный идентификационный номер для Бразилии (RG)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1481">Brazil national identification card (RG)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1482">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1482">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1483">Registro Geral (старый формат): девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1483">Registro Geral (old format): Nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1484">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (новый формат): 11 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1484">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format): 11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1485">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1485">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1486">Registro Geral (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1486">Registro Geral (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1487">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1487">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1488">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1488">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1489">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1489">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1490">точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1490">a period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1491">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1491">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1492">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1492">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1493">одна цифра, которая является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1493">one digit which is a check digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1494">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1494">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1495">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1495">ten digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1496">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1496">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1497">одна цифра, которая является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1497">one digit which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1498">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1498">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1499">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1499">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1500">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1500">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1501">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1501">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1502">функция Func_brazil_rg находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1502">The function Func_brazil_rg finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1503">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_brazil_rg;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1503">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_rg is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1504">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1504">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1505">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1505">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1506">функция Func_brazil_rg находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1506">The function Func_brazil_rg finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1507">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1507">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil National ID Card (RG) -->
<Entity id="486de900-db70-41b3-a886-abdf25af119c" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_rg"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_rg"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_rg"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1511">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1511">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1512">national id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1512">national id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1513">número de rregistro</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1513">número de rregistro</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1514">registro de Iidentidade</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1514">registro de Iidentidade</span></span>

## <a name="bulgaria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1518">Номер водительского удостоверения для Болгарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1518">Bulgaria driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1519">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1519">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1520">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1520">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1521">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1521">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1522">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1522">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1523">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1523">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1524">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1524">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1525">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1525">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1526">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1526">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1527">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1527">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1528">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1528">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="66d39258-94c2-43b2-804b-aa312258e54b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>    
```

## <a name="bulgaria-uniform-civil-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1655">Однородный номер для Болгарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1655">Bulgaria uniform civil number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1656">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1656">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1657">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1657">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1658">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1658">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1659">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1659">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1660">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1660">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1661">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1661">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1662">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1662">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1663">десять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1663">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1664">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1664">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1665">десять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1665">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1666">шесть цифр, соответствующие дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1666">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1667">две цифры, соответствующие порядку рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1667">two digits that correspond to the birth order</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1668">одна цифра, соответствующая полу: четная цифра для самца и нечетная цифра для женщина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1668">one digit that corresponds to gender: An even digit for male and an odd digit for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1669">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1669">one check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1670">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1670">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1671">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1671">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1672">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1672">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1673">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1673">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1674">Функция находит  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1674">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1675">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1675">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1676">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1676">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1677">Функция находит  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1677">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Uniform Civil Number -->
      <Entity id="100d58b1-0a35-4fb1-aa89-e4a86fb53fcc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="bulgaria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1722">Номер паспорта гражданина Болгарии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1722">Bulgaria passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1723">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1723">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1724">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1724">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1725">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1725">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1726">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1726">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1727">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1727">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1728">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1728">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1729">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1729">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1730">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1730">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1731">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1731">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1732">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1732">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1733">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1733">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1734">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1734">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1735">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1735">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1736">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1736">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Bulgaria Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="f7172b82-c588-4216-845e-4e54e397f29a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1756">Номер банковского счета для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1756">Canada bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1757">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1757">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1758">семь или двенадцать цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1758">seven or twelve digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1759">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1759">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1760">Номер банковского счета для Канады — семь или двенадцать цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1760">A Canada Bank Account Number is seven or twelve digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1761">Транзитный номер банковского счета в Канаде имеет указанный ниже формат.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1761">A Canada bank account transit number is:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1762">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1762">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1763">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1763">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1764">три цифры ИЛИ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1764">three digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1765">ноль "0"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1765">a zero "0"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1766">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1766">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1767">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1767">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1768">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1768">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1769">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1769">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1770">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1770">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1771">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1771">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1772">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1772">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1773">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1773">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1774">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1774">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1775">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1775">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1776">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1776">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="552e814c-cb50-4d94-bbaa-bb1d1ffb34de" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number" />
   </Pattern>
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1800">Номер водительского удостоверения для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1800">Canada driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1801">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1801">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1802">Зависит от провинции.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1802">Varies by province</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1803">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1803">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1804">Различные шаблоны, соответствующие провинциям Альберта, Британская Колумбия, Манитоба, Нью-Брансуик, Ньюфаундленд и Лабрадор, Новая Шотландия, Онтарио, Остров Принца Эдуарда, Квебек и Саскачеван.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1804">Various patterns covering Alberta, British Columbia, Manitoba, New Brunswick, Newfoundland/Labrador, Nova Scotia, Ontario, Prince Edward Island, Quebec, and Saskatchewan</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1805">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1805">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1806">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1806">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1807">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1807">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1808">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1808">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1809">функция Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1809">The function Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1810">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1810">A keyword from Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1811">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1811">A keyword from Keyword_canada_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="37186abb-8e48-4800-ad3c-e3d1610b3db0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">

        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />

      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">

      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_newfoundland_labrador_drivers_license_number" />

        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_nova_scotia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_nova_scotia_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ontario_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ontario_drivers_license_name" />

      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_prince_edward_island_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_prince_edward_island_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_quebec_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_quebec_drivers_license_name" />
```

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1948">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1948">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1949">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1949">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1950">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1950">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1951">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1951">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1952">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1952">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1953">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1953">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1954">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1954">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1955">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1955">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1956">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_health_service_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1956">The regular expression Regex_canada_health_service_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1957">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_canada_health_service_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1957">A keyword from Keyword_canada_health_service_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Health Service Number -->
<Entity id="59c0bf39-7fab-482c-af25-00faa4384c94" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_health_service_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_health_service_number" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1969">Номер паспорта гражданина Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1969">Canada passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1971">две буквы в верхнем регистре, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1971">two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1972">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1972">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1975">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1975">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1976">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1976">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1977">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1977">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1978">регулярное выражение Regex_canada_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1978">The regular expression Regex_canada_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-1979">Находится ключевое слово Keyword_canada_passport_number или Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-1979">A keyword from Keyword_canada_passport_number or Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml 
<!-- Canada Passport Number -->
<Entity id="14d0db8b-498a-43ed-9fca-f6097ae687eb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2015">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2015">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2016">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2016">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2017">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2017">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2019">Найдено по крайней мере два ключевых Keyword_canada_phin или Keyword_canada_provinces.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2019">At least two keywords from Keyword_canada_phin or Keyword_canada_provinces are found.</span></span>

```xml
  </Pattern>
```

## <a name="canada-social-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2052">Номер социального страхования для Канады</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2052">Canada social insurance number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2053">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2053">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2054">девять цифр с необязательными дефисами или пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2054">nine digits with optional hyphens or spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2055">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2055">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2056">Формат:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2056">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2057">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2057">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2058">дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2058">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2059">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2059">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2060">дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2060">a hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2061">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2061">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2062">Неформатированные: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2062">Unformatted: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2063">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2063">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2064">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2064">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2065">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2065">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2066">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2066">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2067">Функция Func_canadian_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2067">The function Func_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2068">Выполняются по меньшей мере два из таких условий:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2068">At least two of any combination of the following:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2069">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2069">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2070">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin_collaborative;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2070">A keyword from Keyword_sin_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2071">функция Func_eu_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2071">The function Func_eu_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2072">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2072">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2073">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2073">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2074">функция Func_unformatted_canadian_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2074">The function Func_unformatted_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2075">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_sin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2075">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2076">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2076">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="a2f29c85-ecb8-4514-a610-364790c0773e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_canadian_sin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Func_eu_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_canadian_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="chile-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2101">Номер удостоверения личности для Чили</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2101">Chile identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2102">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2102">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2103">от семи до восьми цифр, а также делегировка контрольной цифры или буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2103">seven to eight digits plus delimiters a check digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2104">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2104">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2105">семь–восемь цифр, а также делегаторы:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2105">seven to eight digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2106">одна–две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2106">one to two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2107">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2107">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2108">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2108">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2109">необязательный период</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2109">an optional period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2110">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2110">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2111">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2111">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2112">одна цифра или буква (без чувствительность к букве), которая является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2112">one digit or letter (not case sensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2113">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2113">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2114">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2114">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2115">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2115">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2116">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2116">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2117">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2117">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2118">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_chile_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2118">A keyword from Keyword_chile_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2119">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2119">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2120">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2120">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2121">функция Func_chile_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2121">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2122">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2122">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Chile Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="4e979794-49a0-407e-a0b9-2c536937b925" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="china-resident-identity-card-prc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2159">Номер удостоверения личности резидента Китая (КНР)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2159">China resident identity card (PRC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2160">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2160">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2161">18 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2161">18 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2162">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2162">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2163">18 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2163">18 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2164">шесть цифр, которые являются кодом адреса</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2164">six digits which are an address code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2165">восемь цифр в формате YYYYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2165">eight digits in the form YYYYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2166">три цифры, которые являются кодом заказа</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2166">three digits which are an order code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2167">одна цифра, которая является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2167">one digit which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2168">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2168">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2169">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2169">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2170">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2170">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2171">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2171">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2172">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2172">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2173">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_china_resident_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2173">A keyword from Keyword_china_resident_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2174">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2174">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2175">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2175">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2176">функция Func_china_resident_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2176">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2177">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2177">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- China Resident Identity Card (PRC) Number -->
<Entity id="c92daa86-2d16-4871-901f-816b3f554fc1" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="credit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2190">Номер кредитной карты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2190">Credit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2191">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2191">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2192">От 14 до 16 цифр, которые могут быть отформатированы или неформатированы (ddd), и которые должны пройти проверку Luhn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2192">14 to 16 digits which can be formatted or unformatted (dddddddddddddddd) and which must pass the Luhn test.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2193">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2193">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2194">Очень сложный и надежный шаблон, который определяет карты всех основных мировых стандартов, включая Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, подарочные карты и карты Diners Club.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2194">Very complex and robust pattern that detects cards from all major brands worldwide, including Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, gift cards, and diner cards.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2195">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2195">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2196">Да (рассчитывается по алгоритму Луна).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2196">Yes, the Luhn checksum</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2197">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2197">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2198">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2198">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2199">Функция Func_credit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2199">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2200">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2200">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2201">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_cc_verification;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2201">A keyword from Keyword_cc_verification is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2202">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_cc_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2202">A keyword from Keyword_cc_name is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2203">функция Func_expiration_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2203">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2204">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2204">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2205">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2205">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2206">функция Func_credit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2206">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2207">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2207">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Credit Card Number -->
<Entity id="50842eb7-edc8-4019-85dd-5a5c1f2bb085" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_verification" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_name" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2467">Номер водительского удостоверения для Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2467">Croatia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2468">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2468">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2469">восемь цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2469">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2470">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2470">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2471">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2471">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2472">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2472">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2473">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2473">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2474">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2474">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2475">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2475">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2476">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2476">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2477">Ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2477">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="005b3ef1-47dd-4e68-bb02-c6db484d00f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2601">Номер удостоверения личности для Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2601">Croatia identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2602">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации для национального идентификационных номеров ЕС и доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2602">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2603">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2603">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2604">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2604">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2605">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2605">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2606">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2606">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2607">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2607">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2608">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2608">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2609">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2609">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2610">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2610">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2611">функция Func_croatia_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2611">The function Func_croatia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2612">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_croatia_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2612">A keyword from Keyword_croatia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Croatia Identity Card Number-->
<Entity id="ff12f884-c20a-4189-b185-34c8e7258d47" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_croatia_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2613">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2613">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="croatia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2643">Номер паспорта гражданина Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2643">Croatia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2644">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2644">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2645">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2645">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2646">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2646">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2647">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2647">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2648">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2648">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2649">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2649">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2650">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2650">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2651">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2651">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2652">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2652">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2653">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2653">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2654">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2654">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2655">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2655">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2656">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2656">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2657">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2657">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Croatia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7d7a729d-32d8-4204-8d01-d5e6a6c25581" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-personal-identification-oib-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2675">Индивидуальный идентификационный номер (OIB) для Хорватии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2675">Croatia personal identification (OIB) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2676">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2676">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2677">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2677">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2678">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2678">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2679">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2679">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2680">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2680">ten digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2681">окончательная цифра — это провероальная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2681">final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2682">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2682">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2683">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2683">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2684">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2684">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2685">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2685">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2686">функция Func_croatia_oib_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2686">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2687">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2687">A keyword from Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2688">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2688">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2689">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2689">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2690">функция Func_croatia_oib_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2690">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2691">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2691">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Croatia Personal Identification (OIB) Number -->
      <Entity id="31983b6d-db95-4eb2-a630-b44bd091968d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2722">Номер водительского удостоверения для Кипра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2722">Cyprus drivers license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2723">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2723">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2724">12 цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2724">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2725">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2725">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2726">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2726">12 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2727">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2727">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2728">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2728">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2729">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2729">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2730">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2730">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2731">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2731">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2732">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2732">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="356fa104-f9ac-4aff-a0e4-2e6e65ea06c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2857">Удостоверение личности для Кипра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2857">Cyprus identity card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2858">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2858">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2859">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2859">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2860">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2860">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2861">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2861">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2862">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2862">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2863">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2863">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2864">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2864">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2865">десять цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2865">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2866">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2866">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2867">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2867">ten digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2868">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2868">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2869">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2869">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2870">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2870">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2871">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2871">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2872">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2872">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2873">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2873">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml 
      <!-- Cyprus Identity Card -->
      <Entity id="3ba8afe5-7a6c-4929-8247-0001b6878438" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2874">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2874">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2878">kim karti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2878">kimlik karti</span></span>

## <a name="cyprus-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2882">Номер паспорта гражданина Кипра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2882">Cyprus passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2883">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2883">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2884">одна буква, за которой следуют 6–8 цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2884">one letter followed by 6-8 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2885">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2885">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2886">одна буква, за которой следуют от шести до восьми цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2886">one letter followed by six to eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2887">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2887">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2888">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2888">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2889">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2889">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2890">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2890">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2891">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2891">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2892">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2892">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2893">Регулярное выражение `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` находит дату в формате ДД/ММ/YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2893">The regular expression `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD/MM/YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2894">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2894">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2895">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2895">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2896">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2896">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>  
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="9193e2e8-7f8c-43c1-a274-ac40d651936f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
