## <a name="cyprus-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2925">Идентификационный номер налога на Кипре</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2925">Cyprus tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2926">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2926">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2927">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2927">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2928">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2928">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2929">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2929">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2930">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2930">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2931">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2931">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2932">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2932">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2933">восемь цифр и одна буква в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2933">eight digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2934">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2934">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2935">восемь цифр и одна буква:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2935">eight digits and one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2936">"0" или "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2936">a "0" or "9"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2937">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2937">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2938">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2938">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2939">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2939">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2940">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2940">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2941">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2941">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2942">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2942">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2943">Функция находит  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2943">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2944">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2944">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2945">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2945">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2946">Функция находит  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2946">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Cyprus Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="40e64bd9-55f3-4a09-9bd6-1db18dced9dd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2964">tic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2964">tic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2965">tin id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2965">tin id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2966">tin no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2966">tin no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2967">tin #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2967">tin#</span></span>

## <a name="czech-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2974">Номер водительского удостоверения для Чешский</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2974">Czech driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2975">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2975">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2976">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2976">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2977">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2977">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2978">восемь букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2978">eight letters and digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2979">буква "E" (без чувствительного к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2979">letter 'E' (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2980">буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2980">a letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2981">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2981">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2982">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2982">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2983">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2983">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2984">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2984">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2985">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2985">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2986">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2986">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2987">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2987">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-2988">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-2988">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
      <Entity id="86b40d3b-d8ea-4c36-aab0-ef9416a6769c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="czech-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3114">Номер паспорта гражданина Чешский</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3114">Czech passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3115">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3115">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3116">восемь цифр без пробелов или делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3116">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3117">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3117">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3118">восемь цифр без пробелов или делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3118">eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3119">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3119">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3120">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3120">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3121">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3121">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3122">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3122">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3123">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3123">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3124">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3124">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3125">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3125">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3126">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3126">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3127">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3127">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3128">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3128">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Czech Republic Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7bcd8ce8-5e92-4bbe-bc92-fa669f0369fa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="czech-personal-identity-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3150">Номер личного удостоверения для чешских пользователей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3150">Czech personal identity number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3151">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3151">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3152">девять цифр с необязательной косой чертой (старый формат) десятью цифрами с необязательной косой чертой (новый формат)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3152">nine digits with optional forward slash (old format) ten digits with optional forward slash (new format)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3153">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3153">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3154">девять цифр (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3154">nine digits (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3155">шесть цифр, которые представляют дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3155">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3156">необязательная косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3156">an optional forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3157">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3157">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3158">десять цифр (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3158">ten digits (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3159">шесть цифр, которые представляют дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3159">six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3160">необязательная косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3160">an optional forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3161">четыре цифры, где последняя цифра является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3161">four digits where last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3162">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3162">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3163">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3163">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3164">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3164">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3165">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3165">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3166">функция Func_czech_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3166">The function Func_czech_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3167">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_czech_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3167">A keyword from Keyword_czech_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3168">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3168">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3169">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3169">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3170">Функция Func_czech_id_card_new_format находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3170">The function Func_czech_id_card_new_format finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3171">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3171">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
      <Entity id="60c0725a-4eb6-455b-9dda-05d8a7396497" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_czech_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3000.000">
          <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
            <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card_new_format" />
          </Pattern>
        </Version>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3218">Номер водительского удостоверения для Дании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3218">Denmark driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3219">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3219">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3220">восемь цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3220">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3221">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3221">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3222">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3222">eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3223">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3223">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3224">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3224">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3225">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3225">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3226">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3226">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3227">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3227">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3228">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3228">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Denmark Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="98a95812-6203-451a-a220-d39870ebef0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3352">Номер паспорта гражданина Дании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3352">Denmark passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3353">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3353">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3354">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3354">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3355">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3355">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3356">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3356">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3357">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3357">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3358">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3358">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3359">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3359">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3360">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3360">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3361">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3361">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3362">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3362">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3363">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date2` находит дату в формате ДД ММ YY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из найденного</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3363">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date2` finds date in the format DD MM YY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3364">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3364">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3365">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3365">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3366">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3366">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Denmark Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="25e8c47e-e6fe-4884-a211-74898f8c0196" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date2" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="denmark-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3386">Персональный идентификационный номер для Дании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3386">Denmark personal identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3387">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3387">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3388">десять цифр, содержащих дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3388">ten digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3389">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3389">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3390">десять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3390">ten digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3391">шесть цифр в формате ДДММАЙ, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3391">six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3392">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3392">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3393">четыре цифры, где последняя цифра является провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3393">four digits where the final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3394">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3394">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3395">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3395">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3396">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3396">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3397">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3397">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3398">Регулярное выражение Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3398">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3399">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_denmark_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3399">A keyword from Keyword_denmark_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3400">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3400">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3401">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3401">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3402">Регулярное выражение Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3402">The regular expression Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3403">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3403">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
      <!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="6c4f2fef-56e1-4c00-8093-88d7a01cf460" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_denmark_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="drug-enforcement-agency-dea-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3475">Номер агентства по правоохранительным органам (DEA)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3475">Drug Enforcement Agency (DEA) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3476">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3476">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3477">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3477">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3478">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3478">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3479">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3479">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3480">одна буква (без регистра) из этого набора возможных букв: abcdefghjklmnprstux, который является регистратором кода</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3480">one letter (not case sensitive) from this set of possible letters: abcdefghjklmnprstux, which is a registrant code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3481">одна буква (без регистра), которая является первой буквой фамилии регистратора или цифрой "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3481">one letter (not case sensitive), which is the first letter of the registrant's last name or digit '9'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3482">семь цифр, последняя из которых является провероной.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3482">seven digits, the last of which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3483">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3483">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3484">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3484">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3485">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3485">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3486">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3486">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3487">функция Func_dea_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3487">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3488">Найдено ключевое `Keyword_dea_number` слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3488">A keyword from `Keyword_dea_number` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3489">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3489">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3490">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3490">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3491">функция Func_dea_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3491">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3492">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3492">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- DEA Number -->
    <Entity id="9a5445ad-406e-43eb-8bd7-cac17ab6d0e4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
      </Pattern>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.1207.000" maxEngineVersion="15.20.3134.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
      <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3135.000">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_dea_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Version>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3493">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3493">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_dea_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3494">Keyword_dea_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3494">Keyword_dea_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3495">dea</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3495">dea</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3496">dea #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3496">dea#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3497">администрирование принудительных органы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3497">drug enforcement administration</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3498">агентство по правоохранительным органам</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3498">drug enforcement agency</span></span>


## <a name="estonia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3499">Номер водительского удостоверения для Эстонии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3499">Estonia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3500">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3500">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3501">две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3501">two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3502">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3502">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3503">две буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3503">two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3504">буквы "ET" (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3504">the letters "ET" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3505">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3505">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3506">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3506">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3507">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3507">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3508">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3508">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3509">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3509">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3510">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3510">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3511">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3511">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="51da8171-da70-4cc1-9d65-055a59ca4f83" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="estonia-personal-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3637">Персональный идентификационный код Для Эстонии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3637">Estonia Personal Identification Code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3638">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3638">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3639">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3639">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3640">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3640">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3641">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3641">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3642">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3642">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3643">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3643">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3644">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3644">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3645">11 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3645">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3646">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3646">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3647">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3647">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3648">одна цифра, соответствующая полу и минуте рождения (нечетное число самца, четное число самка; 1-2: 19-й год; 3-4: 20-й год; 5-6: 21-й год)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3648">one digit that corresponds to sex and century of birth (odd number male, even number female; 1-2: 19th century; 3-4: 20th century; 5-6: 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3649">шесть цифр, соответствующие дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3649">six digits that correspond to date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3650">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру, отделяющие пользователей от одной и той же даты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3650">three digits that correspond to a serial number separating persons born on the same date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3651">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3651">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3652">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3652">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3653">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3653">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3654">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3654">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3655">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3655">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3656">Функция находит  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3656">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3657">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3657">A keyword from  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3658">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3658">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3659">Функция находит  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3659">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Personal Identification Code -->
      <Entity id="bfb26de6-dad5-4d48-ab72-4789cdd0654c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="estonia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3692">Номер паспорта гражданина Эстонии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3692">Estonia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3693">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3693">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3694">одна буква, за которой следуют семь цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3694">one letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3695">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3695">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3696">одна буква, за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3696">one letter followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3697">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3697">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3698">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3698">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3699">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3699">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3700">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3700">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3701">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3701">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3702">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3702">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3703">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3703">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3704">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3704">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3705">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3705">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3706">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3706">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Estonia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61f7073a-509e-425b-a754-bc01bb5d5b8c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="eu-debit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3724">Номер банковской карты для ЕС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3724">EU debit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3725">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3725">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3726">16 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3726">16 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3727">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3727">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3728">Очень сложный и надежный шаблон.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3728">Very complex and robust pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3729">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3729">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3730">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3730">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3731">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3731">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3732">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3732">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3733">Функция Func_eu_debit_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3733">The function Func_eu_debit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3734">Верно по меньшей мере одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3734">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3735">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_eu_debit_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3735">A keyword from Keyword_eu_debit_card is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3736">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_card_terms_dict;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3736">A keyword from Keyword_card_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3737">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_card_security_terms_dict;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3737">A keyword from Keyword_card_security_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3738">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3738">A keyword from Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3739">функция Func_expiration_date находит дату в правильном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3739">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-3740">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-3740">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- EU Debit Card Number -->
    <Entity id="0e9b3178-9678-47dd-a509-37222ca96b42" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_eu_debit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_eu_debit_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_security_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4186">Номер водительского удостоверения для Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4186">Finland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4187">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4187">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4188">десять цифр и букв, содержащих дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4188">ten digits and letters containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4189">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4189">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4190">десять цифр и букв, содержащих дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4190">ten digits and letters containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4191">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4191">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4192">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4192">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4193">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4193">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4194">цифра или буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4194">a digit or letter</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4195">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4195">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4196">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4196">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4197">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4197">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4198">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4198">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4199">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4199">The regular expression  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4200">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4200">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Finland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="bb3b27a3-79bd-4ac4-81a7-f9fca3c7d1a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-european-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4331">Номер медицинского страхования для Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4331">Finland european health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4332">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4332">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4333">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4333">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4334">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4334">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4335">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4335">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4336">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4336">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4337">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4337">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4338">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4338">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4339">20-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4339">20 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4340">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4340">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4341">20-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4341">20-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4342">десять цифр — 8024680246</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4342">ten digits - 8024680246</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4343">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4343">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4344">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4344">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4345">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4345">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4346">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4346">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4347">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4347">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4348">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4348">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4349">Regex Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4349">The regex Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4350">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4350">A keyword from Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finland European Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="60f75aed-81bf-4625-89b0-0846b9248ee7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Finland_European_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4368">Национальный ИД Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4368">Finland national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4369">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4369">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4370">шесть цифр плюс символ, указывающий на время года, а также три цифры плюс контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4370">six digits plus a character indicating a century plus three digits plus a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4371">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4371">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4372">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4372">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4373">шесть цифр в формате DDMMYY, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4373">six digits in the format format DDMMYY which are a date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4374">маркер "-", "+" или "a"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4374">century marker (either '-', '+' or 'a')</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4375">трехзначный персональный идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4375">three-digit personal identification number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4376">цифра или буква (без регистрации буквы), которая является проверокой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4376">a digit or letter (case insensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4377">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4377">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4378">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4378">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4379">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4379">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4380">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4380">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4381">функция Func_finnish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4381">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4382">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_finnish_national_id,</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4382">a keyword from Keyword_finnish_national_id is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4383">контрольнаяума передается</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4383">the checksum passes</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4384">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4384">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4385">функция Func_finnish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4385">the function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4386">контрольнаяума передается</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4386">the checksum passes</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Finnish National ID-->
      <Entity id="338FD995-4CB5-4F87-AD35-79BD1DD926C1" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4435">Номер паспорта гражданина Финляндии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4435">Finland passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4436">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4436">Format</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4437">сочетание девяти букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4437">combination of nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4438">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4438">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4439">сочетание из девяти букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4439">combination of nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4440">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4440">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4441">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4441">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4442">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4442">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4443">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4443">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4444">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4444">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4445">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4445">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4446">регулярное выражение Regex_finland_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4446">The regular expression Regex_finland_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4447">Находится ключевое слово Keywords_eu_passport_number_common или Keyword_finland_passport_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4447">A keyword from Keywords_eu_passport_number_common or Keyword_finland_passport_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Finland Passport Number -->
<Entity id="d1685ac3-1d3a-40f8-8198-32ef5669c7a5" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_finland_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="france-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4468">Номер водительского удостоверения для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4468">France driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4469">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4469">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4470">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4470">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4471">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4471">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4472">12 цифр с проверкой подлинности, чтобы избежать путаницы с похожими шаблонами, например французскими номерами телефонов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4472">12 digits with validation to discount similar patterns such as French telephone numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4473">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4473">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4474">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4474">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4475">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4475">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4476">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4476">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4477">функция Func_french_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4477">the function Func_french_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4478">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_french_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4478">a keyword from Keyword_french_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="18e55a36-a01b-4b0f-943d-dc10282a1824" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_french_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="france-health-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4605">Номер медицинского страхования для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4605">France health insurance number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4606">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4606">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4607">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4607">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4608">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4608">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4609">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4609">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4610">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4610">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4611">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4611">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4612">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4612">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4613">21-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4613">21 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4614">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4614">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4615">21-значный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4615">21 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4616">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4616">ten digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4617">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4617">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4618">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4618">ten digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4619">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4619">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4620">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4620">a digit</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4621">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4621">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4622">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4622">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4623">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4623">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4624">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4624">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4625">Regex Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4625">the regex Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4626">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4626">a keyword from Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Health Insurance Number -->
      <Entity id="9bc2069e-76df-4ff9-ac02-2f519469e236" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_France_Health_Insurance_Number"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4627">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4627">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_health_insurance_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4628">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4628">Keyword_France_health_insurance_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4629">страховая карта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4629">insurance card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4630">carte vitale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4630">carte vitale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4631">carte d'assuré social</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4631">carte d'assuré social</span></span>


## <a name="france-national-id-card-cni"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4632">Национальный удостоверение личности для Франции (CNI)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4632">France national id card (CNI)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4633">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4633">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4634">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4634">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4635">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4635">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4636">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4636">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4637">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4637">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4638">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4638">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4639">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4639">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4640">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4640">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4641">регулярное выражение Regex_france_cni находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4641">The regular expression Regex_france_cni finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4642">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4642">A keyword from Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- France CNI -->
    <Entity id="f741ac74-1bc0-4665-b69b-f0c7f927c0c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="65">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_france_cni" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4643">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4643">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_france_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4644">Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4644">Keywords_france_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4645">card number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4645">card number</span></span>
