- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4648">cni #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4648">cni#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4649">cni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4649">cni</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4650">compte bancaire</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4650">compte bancaire</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4651">national identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4651">national identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4652">national identity</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4652">national identity</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4653">nationalidno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4653">nationalidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4654">numéro d'assurance maladie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4654">numéro d'assurance maladie</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4655">numéro de carte vitale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4655">numéro de carte vitale</span></span>

   
## <a name="france-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4656">Номер паспорта гражданина Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4656">France passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4657">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4657">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4658">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4658">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4659">девять цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4659">nine digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4660">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4660">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4661">девять цифр и букв:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4661">nine digits and letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4662">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4662">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4663">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4663">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4664">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4664">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4665">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4665">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4666">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4666">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4667">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4667">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4668">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4668">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4669">функция Func_fr_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4669">The function Func_fr_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4670">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4670">A keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France Passport Number -->
<Entity id="3008b884-8c8c-4cd8-a289-99f34fc7ff5d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4680">パスポート</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4680">パスポート</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4682">パポк.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4682">パスポートのNum</span></span>

## <a name="france-social-security-number-insee-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4691">Номер социального обеспечения для Франции (INSEE) или эквивалентная идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4691">France social security number (INSEE) or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4692">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации номера социального обеспечения ЕС и эквивалентного ИД и доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4692">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Social Security Number and Equivalent ID sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4693">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4693">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4694">15 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4694">15 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4695">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4695">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4696">Должен соответствовать одному из двух шаблонов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4696">Must match one of two patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4697">13 цифр, за которыми следуют пробелы, за которыми следуют две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4697">13 digits followed by a space followed by two digits</span></span><br/>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4698">или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4698">or</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4699">15 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4699">15 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4700">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4700">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4701">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4701">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4702">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4702">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4703">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 95 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, не отдаленном более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4703">A DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4704">Функция Func_french_insee или Func_fr_insee находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4704">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4705">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_fr_insee;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4705">A keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4706">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4706">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4707">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4707">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4708">Функция Func_french_insee или Func_fr_insee находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4708">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4709">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_fr_insee не находится;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4709">No keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4710">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4710">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France INSEE -->
<Entity id="71f62b97-efe0-4aa1-aa49-e14de253619d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Func_fr_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Func_fr_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4711">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4711">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4717">national identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4717">national identification</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4722">numero d'identite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4722">numero d'identite</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4723">no d'identite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4723">no d'identite</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4724">Нет.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4724">no.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4725">d'identite</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4725">d'identite</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4726">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4726">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4727">social security code</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4727">social security code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4733">numéro d'assurance sociale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4733">numéro d'assurance sociale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4734">numéro de sécu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4734">numéro de sécu</span></span>

## <a name="france-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4736">Идентификационный номер налога для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4736">France tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4737">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4737">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4738">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4738">13 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4739">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4739">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4740">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4740">13 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4741">Одна цифра, которая должна быть 0, 1, 2 или 3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4741">One digit that must be 0, 1, 2, or 3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4742">1 цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4742">1 digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4743">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4743">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4744">2 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4744">2 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4745">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4745">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4746">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4746">3 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4747">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4747">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4748">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4748">3 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4749">пробел (необязательно); </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4749">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4750">3 проверок цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4750">3 check digits</span></span> 

  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4751">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4751">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4752">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4752">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4753">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4753">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4754">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4754">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4755">Функция находит  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4755">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4756">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4756">A keyword from  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4757">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4757">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4758">Функция находит  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4758">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- France Tax Identification Number (numéro SPI.) -->
      <Entity id="ed59e77e-171d-442c-9ec1-88e2ebcb5b0a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4759">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4759">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4760">Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4760">Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4761">numéro d'identification fiscale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4761">numéro d'identification fiscale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4762">tax id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4762">tax id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4763">tax identification no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4763">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4764">налоговый идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4764">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4765">tax no #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4765">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4766">tax no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4766">tax no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4767">налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4767">tax number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4768">налоговый регистрационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4768">tax registration number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4769">ыd #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4769">taxid#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4770">аdno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4770">taxidno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4771">ыdnumber #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4771">taxidnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4772">taxno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4772">taxno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4773">taxnumber #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4773">taxnumber#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4774">taxnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4774">taxnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4775">tin id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4775">tin id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4776">tin no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4776">tin no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4777">tin #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4777">tin#</span></span>


## <a name="france-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4778">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость для Франции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4778">France value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4779">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4779">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4780">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4780">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4781">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4781">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4782">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4782">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4783">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4783">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4784">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4784">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4785">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4785">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4786">13 символов букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4786">13 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4787">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4787">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4788">13 символов букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4788">13 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4789">две буквы — FR (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4789">two letters  - FR (case insensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4790">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4790">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4791">две буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4791">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4792">дополнительное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4792">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4793">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4793">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4794">дополнительное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4794">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4795">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4795">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4796">дополнительное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4796">an optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4797">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4797">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4798">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4798">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4799">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4799">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4800">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4800">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4801">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4801">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4802">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4802">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4803">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4803">A keyword from Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4804">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4804">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4805">Функция Func_france_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4805">The function Func_france_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- France Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="949121e6-ad9f-4379-8731-710342baea78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4806">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4806">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_france_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4807">Keyword_France_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4807">Keyword_France_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4808">номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4808">vat number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4809">vat no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4809">vat no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4810">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4810">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4811">налог на добавленную стоимость</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4811">value added tax</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4812">siren identification no numéro d'identification taxe sur valeur ajoutée</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4812">siren identification no numéro d'identification taxe sur valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4813">taxe valeur ajoutée</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4813">taxe valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4814">taxe sur la valeur ajoutée</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4814">taxe sur la valeur ajoutée</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4815">n° tva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4815">n° tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4816">numéro de tva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4816">numéro de tva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4817">numéro d'identification siren</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4817">numéro d'identification siren</span></span>


## <a name="germany-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4818">Номер водительского удостоверения для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4818">Germany driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4819">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4819">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4820">сочетание 11 цифр и букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4820">combination of 11 digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4821">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4821">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4822">11 цифр и букв (без учета регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4822">11 digits and letters (not case sensitive):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4823">цифра или буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4823">a digit or letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4824">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4824">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4825">шесть цифр или букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4825">six digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4826">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4826">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4827">цифра или буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4827">a digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4828">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4828">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4829">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4829">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4830">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4830">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4831">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4831">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4832">Функция Func_german_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4832">The function Func_german_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4833">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_german_drivers_license_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4833">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4834">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4834">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="91da9335-1edb-45b7-a95f-5fe41a16c63c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_german_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4983">Номер удостоверения личности для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4983">Germany identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4984">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4984">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4985">с 1 ноября 2010 г.: девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4985">since 1 November 2010: Nine letters and digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4986">с 1 апреля 1987 г. по 31 октября 2010 г.: 10 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4986">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010: 10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4987">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4987">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4988">с 1 ноября 2010 г.:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4988">since 1 November 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4989">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4989">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4990">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4990">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4991">с 1 апреля 1987 г. по 31 октября 2010 г.:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4991">from 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4992">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4992">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4993">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4993">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4994">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4994">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4995">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4995">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4996">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4996">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4997">регулярное выражение Regex_germany_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4997">The regular expression Regex_germany_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4998">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_germany_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4998">A keyword from Keyword_germany_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="e577372f-c42e-47a0-9d85-bebed1c237d4" recommendedConfidence="65" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_germany_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_germany_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-4999">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-4999">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5000">Keyword_germany_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5000">Keyword_germany_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5001">ausweis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5001">ausweis</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5002">gpid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5002">gpid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5003">identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5003">identification</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5004">identifikation</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5004">identifikation</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5005">identifizierungsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5005">identifizierungsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5006">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5006">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5007">идентификациный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5007">identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5008">id-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5008">id-nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5009">личный ид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5009">personal id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5010">personalausweis</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5010">personalausweis</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5011">persönliche id nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5011">persönliche id nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5012">persönliche identifikationsnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5012">persönliche identifikationsnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5013">persönliche-id-nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5013">persönliche-id-nummer</span></span>


## <a name="germany-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5014">Номер паспорта гражданина Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5014">Germany passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5015">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5015">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5016">десять цифр или букв</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5016">ten digits or letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5017">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5017">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5018">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5018">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5019">первый символ — это цифра или буква из этого набора (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5019">first character is a digit or a letter from this set (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5020">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5020">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5021">пять цифр или букв из этого набора (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5021">five digits or letters from this set (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5022">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5022">a digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5023">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5023">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5024">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5024">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5025">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5025">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5026">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5026">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5027">функция Func_german_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5027">The function Func_german_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5028">Ключевое слово `Keyword_german_passport` из или `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5028">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5029">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5029">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5030">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5030">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5031">функция Func_german_passport_data находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5031">The function Func_german_passport_data finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5032">Ключевое слово `Keyword_german_passport` из или `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5032">A keyword from `Keyword_german_passport` or `Keywords_eu_passport_number_common` is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5033">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5033">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- German Passport Number -->
    <Entity id="2e3da144-d42b-47ed-b123-fbf78604e52c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport_data" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number_common" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5034">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5034">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_german_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5035">Keyword_german_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5035">Keyword_german_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5044">passeport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5044">passeport no</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number_common"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5045">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5045">Keywords_eu_passport_number_common</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5046">passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5046">passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5047">passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5047">passport #</span></span>

## <a name="germany-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5056">Налоговый идентификационный номер для Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5056">Germany tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5057">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5057">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5058">11 цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5058">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5059">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5059">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5060">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5060">11 digits :</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5061">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5061">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5062">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5062">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5063">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5063">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5064">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5064">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5065">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5065">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5066">Необязательный пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5066">An optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5067">Две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5067">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5068">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5068">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5069">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5069">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5070">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5070">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5071">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5071">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5072">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5072">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5073">Функция находит  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5073">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5074">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5074">A keyword from  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5075">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5075">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5076">Функция находит  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5076">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Germany Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="43316a89-9880-40cf-b980-04bc7eefcec5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5102">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость в Германии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5102">Germany value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5103">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5103">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5104">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5104">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5105">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5105">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5106">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5106">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5107">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5107">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5108">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5108">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5109">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5109">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5110">11 символов букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5110">11 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5111">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5111">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5112">11-символьный буквонумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5112">11-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5113">буква D или d</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5113">a letter D or d</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5114">буква E или e</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5114">a letter E or e</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5115">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5115">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5116">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5116">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5117">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5117">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5118">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5118">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5119">необязательный пробел или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5119">an optional space or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5120">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5120">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5121">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5121">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5122">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5122">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5123">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5123">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5124">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5124">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5125">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5125">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5126">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5126">A keyword from Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5127">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5127">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5128">Функция Func_germany_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5128">The function Func_germany_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Germany Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="db177eb2-8811-4842-bffc-128c14aa219f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5129">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5129">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5130">Keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5130">Keyword_germany_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5131">номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5131">vat number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5133">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5133">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5134">vat# mehrwertsteuer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5134">vat#  mehrwertsteuer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5135">mwst</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5135">mwst</span></span>

## <a name="greece-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5138">Номер водительского удостоверения для Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5138">Greece driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5139">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5139">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5140">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5140">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5141">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5141">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5142">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5142">nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5143">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5143">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5144">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5144">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5145">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5145">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5146">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5146">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5147">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5147">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5148">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5148">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="7a2200b5-aacf-4e3c-ab36-136d3e68b7da" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-national-id-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5274">Карточка национального удостоверения личности для Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5274">Greece national ID card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5275">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5275">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5276">Сочетание 7–8 букв и чисел, а также тире.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5276">Combination of 7-8 letters and numbers plus a dash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5277">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5277">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5278">Семь букв и чисел (старый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5278">Seven letters and numbers (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5279">одна буква (любая буква греческого алфавита);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5279">One letter (any letter of the Greek alphabet)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5280">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5280">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5281">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5281">Six digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5282">Восемь букв и чисел (новый формат):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5282">Eight letters and numbers (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5283">две буквы, которые в прописном виде есть как в греческом, так и латинском алфавите (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5283">Two letters whose uppercase character occurs in both the Greek and Latin alphabets (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5284">тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5284">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5285">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5285">Six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5286">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5286">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5287">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5287">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5288">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5288">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5289">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5289">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5290">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5290">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5291">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_greece_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5291">A keyword from Keyword_greece_id_card is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5292">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5292">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5293">регулярное выражение Regex_greece_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5293">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Greece National ID Card -->
      <Entity id="82568215-1da1-46d3-874a-d2294d81b5ac" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5294">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5294">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_greece_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5295">Keyword_greece_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5295">Keyword_greece_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5296">греческий ид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5296">greek id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5297">греческий национальный ид</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5297">greek national id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5298">личная карточка для греческих личных удостоверений</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5298">greek personal id card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5299">греческий ид полиции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5299">greek police id</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5300">identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5300">identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5301">tautotita</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5301">tautotita</span></span>

## <a name="greece-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5304">Номер паспорта гражданина Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5304">Greece passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5305">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5305">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5306">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5306">Two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5307">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5307">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5308">Две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5308">Two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5309">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5309">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5310">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5310">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5311">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5311">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5312">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5312">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5313">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5313">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5314">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5314">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5315">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM YY (пример — 28 августа 19) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date`</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5315">The regular expression `Regex_greece_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM YY (Example - 28 Aug 19) or a keyword from `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5316">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5316">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5317">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5317">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5318">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5318">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greece Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="7e65eb47-cdf9-4f52-8f90-2a27d5ee67e3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5323">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5323">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5324">passports</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5324">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5325">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5325">passportno</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5328">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5328">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5329">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5329">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5330">passport numbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5330">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_greece_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5331">Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5331">Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5332">αριθμός διαβατηρίου</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5332">αριθμός διαβατηρίου</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5333">αριθμούς διαβατηρίου</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5333">αριθμούς διαβατηρίου</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5334">αριθμός διαβατηριο</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5334">αριθμός διαβατηριο</span></span>


## <a name="greece-social-security-number-amka"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5335">Номер социального обеспечения для Греция (AMKA)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5335">Greece Social Security Number (AMKA)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5336">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5336">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5337">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5337">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5338">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5338">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5339">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5339">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5340">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5340">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5341">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5341">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5342">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5342">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5343">Одиннадцати цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5343">Eleven digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5344">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5344">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5345">6 цифр в качестве даты рождения YYMMDD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5345">6 digits as date of birth YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5346">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5346">4 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5347">проверяемая цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5347">a check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5348">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5348">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5349">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5349">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5350">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5350">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5351">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5351">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5352">Функция находит  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5352">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5353">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5353">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5354">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5354">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5355">Функция находит  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5355">The function  `Func_greece_eu_ssn` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

```xml
      <!-- Greece Social Security Number (AMKA) -->
      <Entity id="e39b03f4-50ea-41ae-af7a-a4b9539596ad" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_greece_eu_ssn" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5356">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5356">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5357">Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5357">Keywords_greece_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5358">ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5358">ssn</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5364">a.m.k.a.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5364">a.m.k.a.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5365">Αριθμού Μητρώου Κοινωνικής Ασφάλισης</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5365">Αριθμού Μητρώου Κοινωνικής Ασφάλισης</span></span>


## <a name="greece-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5366">Идентификационный номер налога для Греция</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5366">Greece tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5367">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5367">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5368">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5368">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5369">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5369">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5370">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5370">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5371">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5371">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5372">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5372">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5373">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5373">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5374">Девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5374">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5375">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5375">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5376">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5376">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5377">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5377">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5378">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5378">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5379">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5379">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5380">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5380">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5381">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5381">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5382">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5382">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Greek Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="15a54a5a-53d4-4080-ad43-a2a4fe1d3bf7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5383">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5383">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5384">Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5384">Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5391">налоговый идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5391">tax identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5392">tax no #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5392">tax no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5393">tax no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5393">tax no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5394">налоговый номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5394">tax number</span></span>
