## <a name="hong-kong-identity-card-hkid-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5411">Номер удостоверения личности в Гонконге (HKID)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5411">Hong Kong identity card (HKID) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5412">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5412">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5413">Сочетание 8–9 букв и чисел, а также необязательные скобки вокруг последнего символа.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5413">Combination of 8-9 letters and numbers plus optional parentheses around the final character</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5414">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5414">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5415">Сочетание 8–9 букв:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5415">Combination of 8-9 letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5416">1–2 буквы (без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5416">1-2 letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5417">шесть цифр; </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5417">Six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5418">последний символ (любая цифра или буква "A") является проверочной цифрой и заключен в скобки (необязательно).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5418">The final character (any digit or the letter A), which is the check digit and is optionally enclosed in parentheses.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5419">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5419">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5420">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5420">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5421">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5421">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5422">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5422">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5423">функция Func_hong_kong_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5423">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5424">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_hong_kong_id_card;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5424">A keyword from Keyword_hong_kong_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5425">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5425">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5426">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5426">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5427">функция Func_hong_kong_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5427">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5428">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5428">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Hong Kong Identity Card (HKID) number -->
<Entity id="e63c28a7-ad29-4c17-a41a-3d2a0b70fd9c" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5468">Номер водительского удостоверения для Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5468">Hungary driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5469">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5469">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5470">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5470">Two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5471">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5471">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5472">Две буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5472">Two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5473">Две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5473">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5474">шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5474">Six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5475">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5475">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5476">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5476">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5477">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5477">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5478">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5478">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5479">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5479">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5480">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5480">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <Entity id="9d31c46b-6e6b-444c-aeb1-6dd7e604bb24" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5481">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5481">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5482">Keywords_eu_driver s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5482">Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5486">driverlicenses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5486">driverlicenses</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5491">driver license</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5491">driver license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5492">driver licenses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5492">driver licenses</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5493">driver licence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5493">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5494">driver licences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5494">driver licences</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5495">driverslic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5495">driverslic</span></span>

## <a name="hungary-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5605">Персональный идентификационный номер для Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5605">Hungary personal identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5606">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5606">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5607">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5607">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5608">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5608">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5609">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5609">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5610">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5610">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5611">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5611">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5612">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5612">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5613">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5613">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5614">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5614">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5615">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5615">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5616">Одна цифра, соответствующая полу (1- и 2-женская, другая цифра также возможна для граждан, которые раньше 1900 г., или граждан с двойным паспортом)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5616">One digit that corresponds to gender (1-male, 2-female, other numbers are also possible for citizens born before 1900 or citizens with double citizenship)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5617">Шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5617">Six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5618">Три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5618">Three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5619">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5619">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5620">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5620">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5621">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5621">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5622">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5622">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5623">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5623">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5624">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5624">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5625">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5625">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5626">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5626">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5627">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5627">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Personal Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="7b5cc218-7046-47d9-80c9-f325b50896ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5629">Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5629">Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5630">id number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5630">id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5631">identification number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5631">identification number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5632">sz ig</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5632">sz ig</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5633">sz.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5633">sz.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5634">ig.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5634">ig.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5635">sz.ig.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5635">sz.ig.</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5637">személyi igazolvány</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5637">személyi igazolvány</span></span>


## <a name="hungary-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5638">Номер паспорта гражданина Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5638">Hungary passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5639">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5639">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5640">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть или семь цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5640">Two letters followed by six or seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5641">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5641">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5642">Две буквы, за которыми следуют шесть или семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5642">Two letters followed by six or seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5643">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5643">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5644">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5644">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5645">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5645">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5646">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5646">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5647">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5647">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5648">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5648">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5649">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM YY (пример — 01 MÁR/MAR 12) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5649">The regular expression `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YY (Example - 01 MÁR/MAR 12) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5650">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5650">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5651">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5651">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5652">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5652">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="5b483910-9aa7-4c99-9917-f4001464bda7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5653">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5653">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5654">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5654">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5655">passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5655">passport#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5656">passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5656">passport #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5657">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5657">passportid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5658">passports</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5658">passports</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5659">passportno</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5659">passportno</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5660">passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5660">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5661">passportnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5661">passportnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5662">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5662">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5663">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5663">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5664">passport numbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5664">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5665">Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5665">Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5666">útlevél száma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5666">útlevél száma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5667">Útlevelek száma</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5667">Útlevelek száma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5668">útlevél szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5668">útlevél szám</span></span>


## <a name="hungary-social-security-number-taj"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5669">Номер социального обеспечения для Венгрии (TAJ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5669">Hungary social security number (TAJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5670">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5670">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5671">Девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5671">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5672">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5672">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5673">Девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5673">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5674">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5674">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5675">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5675">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5676">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5676">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5677">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5677">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5678">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5678">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5679">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5679">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5680">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5680">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5681">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5681">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Social Security Number (TAJ) -->
      <Entity id="0de78315-9537-47f5-95ab-b3e77eba3993" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5682">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5682">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5683">Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5683">Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5685">social security number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5685">social security number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5687">hssn #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5687">hssn#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5691">taj #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5691">taj#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5693">ssn #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5693">ssn#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5694">social security no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5694">social security no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5695">áfa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5695">áfa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5696">közösségi adószám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5696">közösségi adószám</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5697">általános forgalmi adó szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5697">általános forgalmi adó szám</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5698">hozzáadottérték adó</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5698">hozzáadottérték adó</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5699">áfa szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5699">áfa szám</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5700">magyar áfa szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5700">magyar áfa szám</span></span>


## <a name="hungary-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5701">Идентификационный номер налога для Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5701">Hungary tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5702">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5702">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5703">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5703">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5704">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5704">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5705">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5705">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5706">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5706">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5707">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5707">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5708">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5708">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5709">Десять цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5709">Ten digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5710">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5710">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5711">Десять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5711">Ten digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5712">Одна цифра, которая должна быть "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5712">One digit that must be "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5713">восемь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5713">Eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5714">Одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5714">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5715">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5715">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5716">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5716">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5717">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5717">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5718">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5718">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5719">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5719">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5720">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5720">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5721">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5721">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5722">Функция находит  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5722">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Hungary Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="ede42eb4-59d9-49eb-9603-d7853fbda91d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5748">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость для Венгрии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5748">Hungary value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5749">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5749">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5750">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5750">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5751">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5751">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5752">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5752">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5753">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5753">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5754">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5754">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5755">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5755">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5756">10-символьный буквонумерный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5756">10 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5757">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5757">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5758">10 символов букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5758">10 character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5759">2 буквы — HU или hu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5759">2 letters - HU or hu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5760">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5760">optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5761">8 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5761">8 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5762">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5762">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5763">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5763">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5764">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5764">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5765">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5765">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5766">Функция Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5766">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5767">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5767">A keyword from Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5768">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5768">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5769">Функция Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5769">The function Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Hungarian Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="976349a0-683b-477a-90f8-ff0a220d5592" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungarian_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5770">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5770">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_hungary_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5771">Keyword_Hungary_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5771">Keyword_Hungary_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5772">vat</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5772">vat</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5774">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5774">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5775">vatno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5775">vatno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5776">hungarianvatno #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5776">hungarianvatno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5777">tax no.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5777">tax no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5778">налог на добавленную стоимость ( áfa)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5778">value added tax áfa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5779">közösségi adószám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5779">közösségi adószám</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5780">általános forgalmi adó szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5780">általános forgalmi adó szám</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5781">hozzáadottérték adó</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5781">hozzáadottérték adó</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5782">áfa szám</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5782">áfa szám</span></span>


## <a name="india-permanent-account-number-pan"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5783">Постоянный номер учетной записи Для Индии (PAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5783">India permanent account number (PAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5784">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5784">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5785">10 букв или цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5785">10 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5786">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5786">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5787">10 букв или цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5787">10 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5788">Три буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5788">Three letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5789">Буква в C, P, H, F, A, T, B, L, J, G (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5789">A letter in C, P, H, F, A, T, B, L, J, G (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5790">Буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5790">A letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5791">Четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5791">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5792">Буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5792">A letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5793">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5793">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5794">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5794">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5795">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5795">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5796">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5796">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5797">регулярное выражение Regex_india_permanent_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5797">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5798">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_india_permanent_account_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5798">A keyword from Keyword_india_permanent_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5799">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5799">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5800">регулярное выражение Regex_india_permanent_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5800">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>


```xml
      <!-- India Permanent Account Number -->
      <Entity id="2602bfee-9bb0-47a5-a7a6-2bf3053e2804" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_india_permanent_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Version minEngineVersion="15.20.3520.000">
          <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number" />
          </Pattern>
        </Version>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5801">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5801">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_india_permanent_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5802">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5802">Keyword_india_permanent_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5803">Permanent Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5803">Permanent Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5804">PAN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5804">PAN</span></span> 
   
## <a name="india-unique-identification-aadhaar-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5805">Уникальный идентификационный номер (Aadhaar) для Индии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5805">India unique identification (Aadhaar) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5806">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5806">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5807">12 цифр, содержащих необязательные пробелы или тире.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5807">12 digits containing optional spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5808">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5808">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5809">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5809">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5810">Цифра, которая не является 0 или 1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5810">A digit which is not 0 or 1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5811">Три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5811">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5812">необязательный пробел или тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5812">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5813">четыре цифры;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5813">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5814">необязательный пробел или тире;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5814">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5815">последняя цифра — проверочная.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5815">The final digit which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5816">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5816">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5817">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5817">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5818">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5818">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5819">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5819">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5820">функция Func_india_aadhaar находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5820">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5821">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_india_aadhar;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5821">A keyword from Keyword_india_aadhar is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5822">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5822">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- 
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5823">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5823">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5824">функция Func_india_aadhaar находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5824">The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5825">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5825">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- India Unique Identification (Aadhaar) number -->
<Entity id="1ca46b29-76f5-4f46-9383-cfa15e91048f" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_india_aadhar"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5826">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5826">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_india_aadhar"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5827">Keyword_india_aadhar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5827">Keyword_india_aadhar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5828">aadhaar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5828">aadhaar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5829">aadhar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5829">aadhar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5830">aadhar #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5830">aadhar#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5831">uid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5831">uid</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5832">आधार</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5832">आधार</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5833">uidai</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5833">uidai</span></span>
   
## <a name="indonesia-identity-card-ktp-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5834">Номер удостоверения личности (KTP) для Индонезии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5834">Indonesia identity card (KTP) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5835">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5835">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5836">16 цифр, содержащих необязательные точки.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5836">16 digits containing optional periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5837">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5837">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5838">16 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5838">16 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5839">две цифры (код провинции);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5839">Two-digit province code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5840">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5840">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5841">две цифры (код округа или города);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5841">Two-digit regency or city code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5842">две цифры (код района);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5842">Two-digit subdistrict code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5843">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5843">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5844">шесть цифр в формате ДДММГГ (дата рождения);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5844">Six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5845">точка (необязательно);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5845">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5846">четыре цифры.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5846">Four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5847">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5847">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5848">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5848">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5849">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5849">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5850">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5850">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5851">регулярное выражение Regex_indonesia_id_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5851">The regular expression Regex_indonesia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5852">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_indonesia_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5852">A keyword from Keyword_indonesia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Indonesia Identity Card (KTP) Number -->
<Entity id="da68fdb0-f383-4981-8c86-82689d3b7d55" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_indonesia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_indonesia_id_card"/>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5853">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5853">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_indonesia_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5854">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5854">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5855">KTP</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5855">KTP</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5856">Kartu Tanda Penduduk</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5856">Kartu Tanda Penduduk</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5857">Nomor Induk Kependudukan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5857">Nomor Induk Kependudukan</span></span> 
   
## <a name="international-banking-account-number-iban"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5858">Международный номер банковского счета (IBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5858">International banking account number (IBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5859">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5859">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5860">Код страны (две буквы), а также проверочные цифры (две) и номер bban (до 30 символов)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5860">Country code (two letters) plus check digits (two digits) plus bban number (up to 30 characters)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5861">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5861">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5862">Шаблон должен включать в себя все указанные ниже элементы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5862">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5863">Двухбуквенный код страны</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5863">Two-letter country code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5864">Две проверочные цифры (после которых может следовать пробел) </span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5864">Two check digits (followed by an optional space)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5865">1–7 групп из четырех букв или цифр (могут разделяться пробелами)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5865">1-7 groups of four letters or digits (can be separated by spaces)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5866">1–3 буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5866">1-3 letters or digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-p133">Формат для названия каждой из стран немного отличается. Тип конфиденциальной информации IBAN применяется к следующим 60 странам:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-p133">The format for each country is slightly different. The IBAN sensitive information type covers these 60 countries:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5869">ad, ae, al, at, az, ba, be, bg, bh, ch, cr, cy, cz, de, dk, do, ee, es, fi, fo, fr, gb, ge, gi, gl, gr, hr, hu, ie, il, is, it, kw, kz, lb, li, lt, lu, lv, mc, md, me, mk, mr, mt, mu, nl, no, pl, pt, ro, rs, sa, se, si, sk, sm, tn, tr, vg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5869">ad, ae, al, at, az, ba, be, bg, bh, ch, cr, cy, cz, de, dk, do, ee, es, fi, fo, fr, gb, ge, gi, gl, gr, hr, hu, ie, il, is, it, kw, kz, lb, li, lt, lu, lv, mc, md, me, mk, mr, mt, mu, nl, no, pl, pt, ro, rs, sa, se, si, sk, sm, tn, tr, vg</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5870">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5870">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5871">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5871">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5872">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5872">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5873">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5873">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5874">функция Func_iban находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5874">The function Func_iban finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5875">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5875">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="e7dc4711-11b7-4cb0-b88b-2c394a771f0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_iban" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5876">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5876">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5877">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5877">None</span></span>

   
## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-10-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5878">Международная классификация болезни (ICD-10-CM)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5878">International classification of diseases (ICD-10-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5879">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5879">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5880">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5880">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5881">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5881">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5882">Ключевое слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5882">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5883">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5883">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5884">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5884">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5885">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5885">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5886">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5886">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5887">Находится ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_10_updated.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5887">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5888">Находится ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_10_codes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5888">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5889">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5889">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5890">Находится ключевое слово Dictionary_icd_10_ из обновленного.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5890">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_ updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- ICD-10 CM -->
      <Entity id="3356946c-6bb7-449b-b253-6ffa419c0ce7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
        </Pattern>

```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5891">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5891">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5892">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_10_updated ключевых слов, который основан на международной классификации "Болезни", "Десятая редакция", "Модификация с точки зрения правки" [(ICD-10-CM).](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5892">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_10_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases, Tenth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5893">Этот тип ищет только термин, а не страховые коды.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5893">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5894">Любой термин из словаря ключевых слов Dictionary_icd_10_codes, который основан на международной классификации "Болезни", "Десятая редакция", "Модификация" [(ICD-10-CM).](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5894">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_10_codes keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases, Tenth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5895">Этот тип ищет только страховые коды, а не описание.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5895">This type looks only for insurance codes, not the description.</span></span>

## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-9-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5896">Международная классификация болезни (ICD-9-CM)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5896">International classification of diseases (ICD-9-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5897">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5897">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5898">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5898">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5899">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5899">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5900">Ключевое слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5900">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5901">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5901">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5902">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5902">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5903">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5903">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5904">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5904">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5905">Находится ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_9_updated.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5905">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5906">Находится ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_9_codes.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5906">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5907">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5907">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5908">Находится ключевое слово из Dictionary_icd_9_updated.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5908">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <Entity id="fa3f9c74-ee07-4c52-b5f2-085d6b2c0ec4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5909">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5909">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5910">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_9_updated ключевых слов, который основан на международной классификации "Болезни", "Девятая редакция", "Модификация" [(ICD-9-CM).](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5910">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5911">Этот тип ищет только термин, а не страховые коды.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5911">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5912">Любой термин из словаря Dictionary_icd_9_codes ключевых слов, который основан на международной классификации "Болезни", "Девятая редакция", "Модификация" [(ICD-9-CM).](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5912">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_codes keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5913">Этот тип ищет только страховые коды, а не описание.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5913">This type looks only for insurance codes, not the description.</span></span>

## <a name="ip-address"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5914">IP-адрес</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5914">IP address</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5915">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5915">Format</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv4"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5916">IPv4:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5916">IPv4:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5917">Сложный шаблон, ответственный за форматированные (с точками) и неформатированные (без точек) версии IPv4-адресов.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5917">Complex pattern which accounts for formatted (periods) and unformatted (no periods) versions of the IPv4 addresses</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv6"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5918">IPv6:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5918">IPv6:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5919"> Сложный шаблон, ответственный за форматированные номера IPv6 (вместе с двоеточиями).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5919">Complex pattern which accounts for formatted IPv6 numbers (which include colons)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5920">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5920">Pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5921">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5921">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5922">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5922">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5923">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5923">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5924">Для IPv6 политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5924">For IPv6, a DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5925">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv6_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5925">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5926">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5926">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5927">В случае с протоколом IPv4 политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 95 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5927">For IPv4, a DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5928">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv4_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5928">The regular expression Regex_ipv4_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5929">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5929">A keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5930">В случае с протоколом IPv6 политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 95 % верно обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, отдаленном не более чем на 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5930">For IPv6, a DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5931">регулярное выражение Regex_ipv6_address находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5931">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5932">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_ipaddress не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5932">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- IP Address -->
    <Entity id="1daa4ad5-e2dd-4ca4-a788-54722c09efb2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv4_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5933">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5933">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_ipaddress"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5934">Keyword_ipaddress</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5934">Keyword_ipaddress</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5935">IP (ключевое слово с учетом регистра)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5935">IP (this keyword is case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5936">ip address</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5936">ip address</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5937">ip addresses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5937">ip addresses</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5938">internet protocol</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5938">internet protocol</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5939">IP-כתובת ה</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5939">IP-כתובת ה</span></span> 

## <a name="ireland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5940">Номер водительского удостоверения для Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5940">Ireland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5941">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5941">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5942">Шесть цифр, за которыми следуют четыре буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5942">Six digits followed by four letters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5943">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5943">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5944">Шесть цифр и четыре буквы:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5944">Six digits and four letters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5945">Шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5945">Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5946">Четыре буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5946">Four letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5947">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5947">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5948">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5948">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5949">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5949">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5950">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5950">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5951">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5951">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5952">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5952">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Ireland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="e01bccd9-eb4d-414f-ace1-e9b6a4c4a2ca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-5953">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-5953">Keywords</span></span>
