## <a name="ireland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6076">Номер паспорта гражданина Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6076">Ireland passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6077">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6077">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6078">Две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6078">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6079">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6079">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6080">Две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6080">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6081">две цифры или буквы (без учета регистра);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6081">Two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6082">семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6082">Seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6083">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6083">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6084">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6084">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6085">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6085">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6086">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6086">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6087">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6087">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6088">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6088">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6089">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM ГГ ГГ (пример — 01 BEA/MAY 1988) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6089">The regular expression `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 BEA/MAY 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6090">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6090">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6091">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6091">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6092">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6092">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Ireland Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="a2130f27-9ee2-4103-84f9-a6b1ee7d0cbf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-personal-public-service-pps-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6116">Номер личной службы (PPS) для Ирландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6116">Ireland personal public service (PPS) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6117">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6117">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6118">Старый формат (до 31 декабря 2012 г.):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6118">Old format (until 31 Dec 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6119">семь цифр, за которыми следуют 1–2 буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6119">seven digits followed by 1-2 letters</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6120">Новый формат (1 января 2013 г. и после):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6120">New format (1 Jan 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6121">семь цифр, за которыми следуют две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6121">seven digits followed by two letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6122">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6122">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6123">Старый формат (до 31 декабря 2012 г.):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6123">Old format (until 31 Dec 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6124">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6124">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6125">от одной до двух букв (без чувствительность к буквам);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6125">one to two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6126">Новый формат (1 января 2013 г. и после):</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6126">New format (1 Jan 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6127">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6127">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6128">буква (без чувствительной к букве), которая является алфавитной провероной цифрой</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6128">a letter (not case sensitive) which is an alphabetic check digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6129">Необязательная буква в диапазоне A-I или W</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6129">An optional letter in the range A-I, or “W”</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6130">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6130">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6131">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6131">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6132">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6132">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6133">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6133">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6134">функция Func_ireland_pps находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6134">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6135">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6135">A keyword from Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6136">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6136">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6137">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6137">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6138">функция Func_ireland_pps находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6138">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6139">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6139">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ireland Personal Public Service (PPS) Number -->
      <Entity id="1cdb674d-c19a-4fcf-9f4b-7f56cc87345a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85" relaxProximity="true">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="israel-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6184">Номер банковского счета для Израиль</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6184">Israel bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6185">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6185">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6186">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6186">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6187">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6187">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6188">Формат:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6188">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6189">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6189">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6190">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6190">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6191">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6191">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6192">тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6192">a dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6193">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6193">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6194">Неформатированные:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6194">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6195">	13 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6195">13 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6196">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6196">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6197">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6197">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6198">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6198">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6199">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6199">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6200">регулярное выражение Regex_israel_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6200">The regular expression Regex_israel_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6201">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_israel_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6201">A keyword from Keyword_israel_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="7d08b2ff-a0b9-437f-957c-aeddbf9b2b25" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_israel_bank_account_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_israel_bank_account_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6202">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6202">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_israel_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6203">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6203">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6204">Bank Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6204">Bank Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6205">Bank Account</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6205">Bank Account</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6206">Account Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6206">Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6207">מספר חשבון בנק</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6207">מספר חשבון בנק</span></span> 
   
## <a name="israel-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6208">Национальный идентификационный номер для Израиля</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6208">Israel national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6209">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6209">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6210">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6210">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6211">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6211">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6212">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6212">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6213">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6213">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6214">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6214">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6215">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6215">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6216">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6216">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6217">функция Func_israeli_national_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6217">The function Func_israeli_national_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6218">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Israel_National_ID;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6218">A keyword from Keyword_Israel_National_ID is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6219">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6219">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel National ID Number -->
<Entity id="e05881f5-1db1-418c-89aa-a3ac5c5277ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_israeli_national_id_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Israel_National_ID" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6220">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6220">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="italy-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6238">Номер водительского удостоверения для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6238">Italy driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6239">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6239">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6240">сочетание 10 букв и цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6240">a combination of 10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6241">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6241">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6242">сочетание из 10 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6242">a combination of 10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6243">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6243">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6244">буква "A" или "V" (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6244">the letter "A" or "V" (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6245">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6245">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6246">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6246">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6247">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6247">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6248">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6248">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6249">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6249">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6250">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6250">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6251">регулярное выражение Regex_italy_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6251">The regular expression Regex_italy_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6252">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6252">A keyword from Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Italy Driver's license Number -->
<Entity id="97d6244f-9157-41bd-8e0c-9d669a5c4d71" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6253">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6253">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_italy_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6254">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6254">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6255">numero di patente</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6255">numero di patente</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6256">patente di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6256">patente di guida</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6257">patente guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6257">patente guida</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6258">patenti di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6258">patenti di guida</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6259">patenti guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6259">patenti guida</span></span>

## <a name="italy-fiscal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6260">Финансовый код Для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6260">Italy fiscal code</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6261">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6261">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6262">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6262">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6263">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6263">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6264">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6264">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6265">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6265">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6266">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6266">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6267">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6267">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6268">16-значное сочетание букв и цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6268">a 16-character combination of letters and digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6269">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6269">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6270">16-значное сочетание букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6270">A 16-character combination of letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6271">три буквы, соответствующие первым трем consonants в имени семейства</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6271">three letters that correspond to the first three consonants in the family name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6272">три буквы, соответствующие первому, третьему и четвертому consonants в первом имени</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6272">three letters that correspond to the first, third, and fourth consonants in the first name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6273">две цифры, соответствующие последним цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6273">two digits that correspond to the last digits of the birth year</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6274">одна буква, соответствующая букве месяца рождения, буквы используются в алфавитном порядке, но используются только буквы A в E, H, L, M, P, R to T (таким образом, январь A, а октябрь — R)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6274">one letter that corresponds to the letter for the month of birth—letters are used in alphabetical order, but only the letters A to E, H, L, M, P, R to T are used (thus, January is A and October is R)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6275">две цифры, соответствующие дню месяца рождения, чтобы различать полы, 40 добавляется в день рождения для</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6275">two digits that correspond to the day of the month of birth—in order to differentiate between genders, 40 is added to the day of birth for women</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6276">четыре цифры, соответствующие коду региона, относя к замурованию человека (коды на территории страны используются для внешних стран)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6276">four digits that corresponds to the area code specific to the municipality where the person was born (country-wide codes are used for foreign countries)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6277">одна цифра четности</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6277">one parity digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6278">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6278">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6279">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6279">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6280">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6280">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6281">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6281">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6282">Функция находит  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6282">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6283">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6283">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6284">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6284">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6285">Функция находит  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6285">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Fiscal Code -->
      <Entity id="4cd79172-8da9-4ff5-9188-98b1e7e2eca6" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="italy-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6320">Номер паспорта гражданина Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6320">Italy passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6321">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6321">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6322">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6322">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6323">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6323">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6324">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6324">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6325">две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6325">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6326">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6326">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6327">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6327">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6328">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6328">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6329">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6329">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6330">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6330">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6331">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6331">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6332">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6332">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6333">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM ГГ ГГ (пример — 01 GEN/JAN 1988) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6333">The regular expression `Regex_italy_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 01 GEN/JAN 1988) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6334">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6334">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6335">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6335">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6336">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6336">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Italy Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="39811019-4750-445f-b26d-4c0e6c431544" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6337">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6337">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6342">passports</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6342">passports</span></span>

## <a name="italy-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6360">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость для Италия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6360">Italy value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6361">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6361">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6362">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6362">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6363">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6363">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6364">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6364">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6365">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6365">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6366">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6366">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6367">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6367">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6368">13-символьный буквонумерный шаблон с необязательными делетерами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6368">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6369">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6369">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6370">13 символов букв и цифр с необязательными делетерами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6370">13 character alphanumeric pattern with optional delimiters:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6371">I или i</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6371">I or i</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6372">T или t</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6372">T or t</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6373">дополнительное пространство, точка, дефис или запятая</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6373">optional space, dot, hyphen or comma</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6374">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6374">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6375">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6375">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6376">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6376">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6377">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6377">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6378">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6378">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6379">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6379">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6380">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6380">A keyword from Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6381">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6381">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6382">Функция Func_italy_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6382">The function Func_italy_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Italy Value Added Tax -->
      <Entity id="26a8cc07-2283-4a2a-ab1d-4ab643c4c67f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6383">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6383">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6384">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6384">Keyword_italy_value_added_tax_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6385">номер плательщика НДС</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6385">vat number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6387">vat #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6387">vat#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6388">iva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6388">iva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6389">iva #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6389">iva#</span></span>


## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6390">Номер банковского счета для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6390">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6391">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6391">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6392">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6392">seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6393">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6393">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6394">номер банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6394">bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6395">семь или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6395">seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6396">код филиала банковского счета:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6396">bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6397">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6397">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6398">пробел или тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6398">a space or dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6399">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6399">three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6400">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6400">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6401">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6401">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6402">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6402">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6403">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6403">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6404">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6404">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6405">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6405">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6406">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6406">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6407">функция Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6407">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6408">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6408">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6409">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6409">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6410">функция Func_jp_bank_account находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6410">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6411">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_bank_account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6411">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6412">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6412">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="japan-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6458">Номер водительского удостоверения для Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6458">Japan driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6459">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6459">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6460">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6460">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6461">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6461">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6462">12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6462">12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6463">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6463">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6464">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6464">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6465">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6465">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6466">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6466">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6467">функция Func_jp_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6467">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6468">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6468">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-my-number---corporate"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6506">Мой номер для Японии — корпоративный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6506">Japan My Number - Corporate</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6507">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6507">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6508">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6508">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6509">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6509">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6510">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6510">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6511">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6511">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6512">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6512">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6513">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6513">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6514">13-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6514">13 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6515">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6515">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6516">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6516">13 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6517">одна цифра от одной до девяти</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6517">one digit from one to nine</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6518">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6518">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6519">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6519">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6520">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6520">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6521">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6521">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6522">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6522">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6523">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6523">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6524">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6524">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6525">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6525">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6526">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_corporate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6526">The function Func_japanese_my_number_corporate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Corporate -->
      <Entity id="9e0eaf79-ff20-4ffb-b3e4-e7368d5db6ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_corporate" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-my-number---personal"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6539">Мой номер для Японии — личный</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6539">Japan My Number - Personal</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6540">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6540">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6541">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6541">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6542">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6542">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6543">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6543">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6544">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6544">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6545">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6545">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6546">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6546">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6547">12-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6547">12 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6548">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6548">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6549">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6549">12 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6550">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6550">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6551">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6551">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6552">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6552">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6553">необязательный пробел, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6553">an optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6554">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6554">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6555">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6555">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6556">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6556">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6557">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6557">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6558">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6558">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6559">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6559">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6560">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6560">A keyword from Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6561">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6561">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6562">Функция Func_japanese_my_number_personal находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6562">The function Func_japanese_my_number_personal finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Japanese My Number – Personal -->
      <Entity id="98da8e66-7299-4ebd-9f82-c871ab37d3ef" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_japanese_my_number_personal" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6568">共通番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6568">共通番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6569">マイナンバーカード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6569">マイナンバーカード</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6570">マイナンバーカード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6570">マイナンバーカード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6571">個人番号カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6571">個人番号カード</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6573">個人識別ナンバー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6573">個人識別ナンバー</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6574">通知カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6574">通知カード</span></span>

   
## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6575">Номер паспорта гражданина Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6575">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6576">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6576">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6577">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6577">two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6578">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6578">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6579">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6579">two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6580">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6580">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6581">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6581">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6582">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6582">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6583">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6583">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6584">функция Func_jp_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6584">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6585">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6585">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="75177310-1a09-4613-bf6d-833aae3743f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6595">パスポート＃</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6595">パスポート＃</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6596">パスポート #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6596">パスポート#</span></span>

## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6602">Номер карты для проживания в Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6602">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6603">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6603">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6604">12 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6604">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6605">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6605">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6606">12 букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6606">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6607">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6607">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6608">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6608">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6609">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6609">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6610">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6610">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6611">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6611">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6612">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6612">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6613">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6613">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6614">Регулярное выражение Regex_jp_residence_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6614">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6615">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_residence_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6615">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6616">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6616">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_residence_card_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6617">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6617">Keyword_jp_residence_card_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6618">Номер карты для проживания</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6618">Residence card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6619">Карты проживания нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6619">Residence card no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6620">Карточка для проживания #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6620">Residence card #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6621">在留カード番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6621">在留カード番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6622">在留カード</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6622">在留カード</span></span>

## <a name="japan-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6624">Номер регистрации резидента Японии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6624">Japan resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6625">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6625">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6626">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6626">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6627">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6627">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6628">11 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6628">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6629">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6629">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6630">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6630">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6631">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6631">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6632">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6632">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6633">функция Func_jp_resident_registration_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6633">The function Func_jp_resident_registration_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6634">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6634">A keyword from Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_resident_registration_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6639">Resident Registration No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6639">Resident Registration No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6640">Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6640">Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6641">Residents Basic Registry No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6641">Residents Basic Registry No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6642">Basic Resident Register No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6642">Basic Resident Register No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6643">外国人登録証明書番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6643">外国人登録証明書番号</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6644">証明書番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6644">証明書番号</span></span>

## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6647">Номер социального страхования для Японии (SIN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6647">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6648">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6648">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6649">7–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6649">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6650">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6650">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6651">7–12 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6651">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6652">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6652">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6653">дефис (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6653">a hyphen (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6654">шесть цифр ИЛИ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6654">six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6655">7–12 последовательных цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6655">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6656">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6656">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6657">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6657">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6658">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6658">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6659">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6659">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6660">функция Func_jp_sin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6660">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6661">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6661">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6662">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6662">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6663">функция Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6663">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6664">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_jp_sin.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6664">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6680">介護保険被保険者番号</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6680">介護保険被保険者番号</span></span>

## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6685">Номер водительского удостоверения для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6685">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6686">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6686">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6687">три буквы, за которыми следуют шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6687">three letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6688">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6688">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6689">три буквы и шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6689">three letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6690">три буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6690">three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6691">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6691">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6692">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6692">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6693">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6693">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6694">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6694">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6695">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6695">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6696">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6696">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6697">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6697">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="ec996de0-30f2-46b1-b192-4d2ff8805fa7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
