## <a name="latvia-personal-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6822">Персональный код для Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6822">Latvia personal code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6823">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6823">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6824">11 цифр и необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6824">11 digits and an optional hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6825">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6825">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6826">Старый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6826">Old format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6827">11 цифр и дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6827">11 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6828">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (ДДММАЙ)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6828">six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6829">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6829">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6830">одна цифра, соответствующая годовщине рождения ("0" для 19-го, "1" для 20-го и "2" для 21-го)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6830">one digit that corresponds to the century of birth ("0" for 19th century, "1" for 20th century, and "2" for 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6831">четыре цифры, генерируемые случайным образом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6831">four digits, randomly generated</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6832">Новый формат</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6832">New format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6833">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6833">11 digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6834">Две цифры "32"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6834">Two digits "32"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6835">девять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6835">Nine digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6836">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6836">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6837">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6837">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6838">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6838">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6839">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6839">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6840">Функция или  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` regex находит `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6840">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6841">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6841">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6842">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6842">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6843">Функция или  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` regex находит `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6843">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` or the regex `Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="03fcf763-27c2-49ed-9422-2641c6c895c9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_national_id_card_new_format" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>

```

## <a name="latvia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6906">Номер паспорта гражданина Латвии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6906">Latvia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6907">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6907">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6908">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6908">two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6909">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6909">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6910">две буквы или цифры, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6910">two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6911">две цифры или буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6911">two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6912">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6912">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6913">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6913">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6914">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6914">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6915">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6915">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6916">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6916">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6917">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6917">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6918">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6918">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6919">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6919">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6920">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6920">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6921">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6921">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6922">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6922">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Latvia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="23ae25ec-cc28-421b-b77a-3054eadf1ede" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6945">Номер водительского удостоверения для Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6945">Lithuania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6946">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6946">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6947">восемь цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6947">eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6948">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6948">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6949">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6949">eight digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6950">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6950">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6951">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6951">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6952">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6952">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6953">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6953">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6954">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6954">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6955">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6955">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="86f7628b-e0f4-4dc3-9fbc-e4300e4c7d78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6956">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6956">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6957">Keywords_eu_driver s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6957">Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-6958">driverlic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-6958">driverlic</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7087">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7087">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7088">11 цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7088">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7089">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7089">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7090">11 цифр без пробелов и селитров:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7090">11 digits without spaces and delimiters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7091">одна цифра (1–6), соответствующая полу и возрасту человека при рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7091">one digit (1-6) that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7092">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7092">six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7093">три цифры, соответствующие серийному номеру даты рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7093">three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7094">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7094">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7095">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7095">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7096">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7096">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7097">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7097">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7098">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7098">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7099">Функция находит  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7099">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7100">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7100">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7101">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7101">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7102">Функция находит  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7102">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Personal Code -->
      <Entity id="cd6d3786-8ec3-4524-a2cf-1e0095379171" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7137">Номер паспорта гражданина Литвы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7137">Lithuania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7138">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7138">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7139">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов или селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7139">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7140">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7140">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7141">восемь цифр или букв (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7141">eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7142">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7142">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7143">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7143">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7144">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7144">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7145">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7145">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7146">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7146">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7147">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7147">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7148">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date3` находит дату в формате ДД ММ YYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7148">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7149">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7149">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7150">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7150">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7151">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7151">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Lithuania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="1b79900f-047b-4c3f-846f-7d73b5534bce" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7169">дата проблемы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7169">date of issue</span></span>

## <a name="luxemburg-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7171">Номер водительского удостоверения Химнюка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7171">Luxemburg driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7172">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7172">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7173">шесть цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7173">six digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7174">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7174">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7175">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7175">six digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7176">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7176">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7177">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7177">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7178">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7178">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7179">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7179">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7180">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7180">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7181">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7181">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="89daf717-1544-4860-9a2e-fc9166dd8852" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7182">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7182">Keywords</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7312">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7312">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7313">13 цифр без пробелов или селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7313">13 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7314">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7314">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7315">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7315">13 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7316">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7316">11 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7317">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7317">two check digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7318">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7318">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7319">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7319">yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7320">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7320">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7321">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7321">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7322">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7322">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7323">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7323">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7324">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7324">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7325">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7325">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 


```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="aaf661ed-29ec-426d-8bf9-880cad298ebb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7348">Номер паспорта Химмюна</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7348">Luxemburg passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7349">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7349">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7350">восемь цифр или букв без пробелов или селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7350">eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7351">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7351">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7352">восемь цифр или букв (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7352">eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7353">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7353">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7354">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7354">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7355">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7355">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7356">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7356">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7357">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7357">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7358">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7358">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7359">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date3` находит дату в формате ДД ММ YYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7359">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date3` finds date in the format DD MM YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7360">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7360">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7361">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7361">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7362">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7362">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="81d5c027-bed9-4421-91a0-3b2e55b3eb85" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date3" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number-non-natural-persons"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7394">Национальный идентификационный номер для Фемнеса (не является лицом)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7394">Luxemburg national identification number (non natural persons)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7395">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7395">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7396">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7396">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7397">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7397">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7398">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7398">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7399">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7399">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7400">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7400">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7401">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7401">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7402">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7402">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7403">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7403">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7404">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7404">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7405">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7405">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7406">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7406">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7407">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7407">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7408">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7408">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7409">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7409">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7410">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7410">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7411">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7411">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7412">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7412">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7413">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7413">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7414">Функция находит  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7414">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Luxemburg National Identification Number (Non-natural persons) -->
      <Entity id="84bffa3a-d805-4788-a613-b1e4df3804cf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number_non_natural" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malaysia-identification-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7454">Номер идентификационных карт для Малайзии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7454">Malaysia identification card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7455">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7455">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7456">12 цифр, содержащих необязательные дефисы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7456">12 digits containing optional hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7457">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7457">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7458">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7458">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7459">шесть цифр в формате YYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7459">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7460">Тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7460">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7461">двух буквный код места рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7461">two-letter place-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7462">Тире (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7462">a dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7463">три случайные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7463">three random digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7464">однозначный код пола</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7464">one-digit gender code</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7465">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7465">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7466">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7466">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7467">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7467">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7468">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7468">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7469">регулярное выражение Regex_malaysia_id_card_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7469">The regular expression Regex_malaysia_id_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7470">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7470">A keyword from Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Malaysia ID Card Number -->
</Entity>
      <Entity id="7f0e921c-9677-435b-aba2-bb8f1013c749" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malaysia_id_card_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7488">mykad</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7488">mykad</span></span>

## <a name="malta-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7497">Номер водительского удостоверения для Мальты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7497">Malta driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7498">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7498">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7499">Сочетание двух символов и шести цифр в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7499">Combination of two characters and six digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7500">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7500">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7501">сочетание двух символов и шести цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7501">combination of two characters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7502">два символа (цифры или буквы, без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7502">two characters (digits or letters, not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7503">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7503">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7504">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7504">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7505">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7505">a space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7506">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7506">three digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7507">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7507">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7508">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7508">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7509">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7509">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7510">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7510">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7511">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7511">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7512">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7512">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="a3bdaa4a-8371-4735-8fa5-56ee0fb4afc4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7513">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7513">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7514">Keywords_eu_driver s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7514">Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7515">driverlic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7515">driverlic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7516">driverlics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7516">driverlics</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7517">driverlicense</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7517">driverlicense</span></span>

## <a name="malta-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7636">Номер удостоверения личности для Мальты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7636">Malta identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7637">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7637">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7638">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7638">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7639">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7639">communication compliance policies</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7641">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7641">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7642">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7642">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7643">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7643">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7644">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7644">seven digits followed by one letter</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7645">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7645">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7646">семь цифр, за которыми следует одна буква:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7646">seven digits followed by one letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7647">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7647">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7648">одна буква в "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (без чувствительность к делу)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7648">one letter in "M, G, A, P, L, H, B, Z" (case insensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7649">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7649">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7650">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7650">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7651">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7651">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7652">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7652">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7653">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7653">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7654">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7654">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7655">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7655">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7656">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7656">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Identity Card Number -->
      <Entity id="854b36b3-a388-4ac8-a4ec-677c2b5e4356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7673">Номер паспорта гражданина Мальты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7673">Malta passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7674">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7674">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7675">семь цифр без пробелов или делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7675">seven digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7676">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7676">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7677">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7677">seven digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7678">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7678">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7679">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7679">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7680">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7680">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7681">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7681">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7682">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7682">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7683">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7683">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7684">Найдено ключевое `Keywords_eu_passport_date` слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7684">A keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7685">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7685">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7686">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7686">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7687">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7687">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="b2b21198-48f9-4d13-b2a5-03969bff0fb8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_malta_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7700">Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7700">Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number</span></span>

## <a name="malta-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7707">Идентификационный номер налога на Мальте</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7707">Malta tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7708">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7708">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7709">Для граждан Тайваня:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7709">For Maltese nationals:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7710">семь цифр и одна буква в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7710">seven digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7711">Неконтюзские граждане и подмайства:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7711">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7712">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7712">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7713">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7713">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7714">Граждане Тайваня: семь цифр и одна буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7714">Maltese nationals: seven digits and one letter</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7715">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7715">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7716">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7716">one letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7717">Негитюзские граждане и сущностями, не относягими к сущностям: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7717">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: nine digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7718">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7718">nine digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7719">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7719">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7720">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7720">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7721">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7721">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7722">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7722">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7723">Regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7723">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number`  or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7724">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7724">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7725">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7725">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7726">Regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` или `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7726">The regex  `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number` or `Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Malta Tax ID Number -->
      <Entity id="ec830c63-65f4-45d0-9d8c-910dc8334b20" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number_non_maltese_national" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7727">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7727">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7728">Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7728">Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7729">citizen service number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7729">citizen service number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7730">id9-taxxa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7730">id tat-taxxa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7731">identifika numru tal-jett</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7731">identifika numru tal-biljett</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7732">kodiċi numerali personali</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7732">kodiċi numerali personali</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7733">numru ta 'identifzzjoni personali</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7733">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni personali</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7734">numru ta 'identifzzjonident-taxxa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7734">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni tat-taxxa</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7735">numru ta 'identifzzjoni uniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7735">numru ta 'identifikazzjoni uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7736">numru ta' identità uniku</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7736">numru ta' identità uniku</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7737">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7737">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-citizens-service-bsn-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7759">Номер службы гражданина Нидерландов (BSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7759">Netherlands citizen's service (BSN) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7760">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7760">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7761">восемь-девять цифр, содержащих необязательные пробелы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7761">eight-nine digits containing optional spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7762">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7762">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7763">восемь-девять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7763">eight-nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7764">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7764">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7765">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7765">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7766">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7766">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7767">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7767">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7768">две-три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7768">two-three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7769">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7769">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7770">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7770">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7771">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7771">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7772">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7772">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7773">функция Func_netherlands_bsn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7773">The function Func_netherlands_bsn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7774">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_netherlands_bsn;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7774">A keyword from Keyword_netherlands_bsn is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7775">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7775">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Citizen's Service (BSN) Number -->
      <Entity id="c5f54253-ef7e-44f6-a578-440ed67e946d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_bsn" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7799">Номер водительского удостоверения для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7799">Netherlands driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7800">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7800">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7801">десять цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7801">ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7802">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7802">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7803">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7803">ten digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7804">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7804">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7805">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7805">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7806">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7806">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7807">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7807">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7808">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7808">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7809">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7809">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="6247fbea-ab80-4be5-8233-308b7c031401" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7937">Номер паспорта гражданина Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7937">Netherlands passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7938">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7938">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7939">девять букв или цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7939">nine letters or digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7940">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7940">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7941">девять букв или цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7941">nine letters or digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7942">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7942">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7943">неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7943">not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7944">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7944">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7945">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7945">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7946">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7946">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7947">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7947">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7948">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` ДД MMM/MMM YYYY (пример — 26 MAA/MAR 2012)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7948">The regular expression `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format  DD MMM/MMM YYYY (Example - 26 MAA/MAR 2012)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7949">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7949">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7950">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7950">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7951">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7951">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="61786727-bafd-45f6-94d9-888d815e228e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_date" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7969">Налоговый идентификационный номер для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7969">Netherlands tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7970">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7970">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7971">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7971">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7972">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7972">communication compliance policies</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7976">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7976">Format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7978">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7978">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7979">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7979">nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7981">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7981">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7982">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7982">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7983">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7983">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7984">Функция находит  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7984">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7985">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7985">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7986">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7986">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-7987">Функция находит  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-7987">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="01f42a64-eba7-4892-a67b-398237e4ade2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
