## <a name="netherlands-value-added-tax-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8025">Номер налога на добавленную стоимость для Нидерландов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8025">Netherlands value added tax number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8026">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8026">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8027">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8027">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8028">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8028">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8029">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8029">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8030">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8030">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8031">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8031">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8032">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8032">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8033">14-символьный буквонумерный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8033">14 character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8034">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8034">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8035">14-символьный буквонумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8035">14-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8036">N или n</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8036">N or n</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8037">L или l</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8037">L or l</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8038">дополнительное пространство, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8038">optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8039">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8039">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8040">дополнительное пространство, точка или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8040">optional space, dot or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8041">B или b</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8041">B or b</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8042">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8042">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8043">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8043">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8044">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8044">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8045">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8045">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8046">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8046">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8047">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8047">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8048">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8048">A keyword from Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8049">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8049">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8050">Функция Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8050">The function Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Netherlands Value Added Tax Number -->
      <Entity id="4f320d9b-4972-41ae-b337-88d499bb1ade" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_value_added_tax_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8056">налоговый возврат на носимый tafoege</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8056">wearde tafoege tax getal</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8059">Номер банковского счета для Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8059">New Zealand bank account number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8060">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8060">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8061">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8061">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8062">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8062">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8063">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8063">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8064">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8064">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8065">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8065">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8066">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8066">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8067">Шаблон из 14-16 цифр с необязательными делегаторами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8067">14 to 16 digit pattern with optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8068">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8068">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8069">Шаблон из 14–16 цифр с необязательными делегаторами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8069">14 to 16 digit pattern with optional delimiter:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8070">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8070">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8071">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8071">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8072">три-четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8072">three to four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8073">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8073">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8074">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8074">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8075">необязательный дефис или пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8075">an optional hyphen or space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8076">две-три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8076">two to three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8077">дефис или пробел для параметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8077">an options hyphen or space</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8079">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8079">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8080">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8080">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8081">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8081">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8082">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8082">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8083">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8083">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8084">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8084">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8085">Функция Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8085">The function Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Bank Account Number -->
      <Entity id="1a97fc2b-dd2f-48f1-bc4e-2ddf25813956" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zFealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_bank_account_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8095">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8095">data loss prevention policies</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8097">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8097">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8098">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8098">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8099">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8099">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8101">восьми символьный букво-цифровая схема</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8101">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8102">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8102">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8103">восьми символьный букво-цифровая схема</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8103">eight character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8108">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8108">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8109">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8109">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8110">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8110">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8111">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8111">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8112">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8112">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8113">Функция Func_newzealand_driver_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8113">The function Func_newzealand_driver_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Driver License Number -->
      <Entity id="1924b377-d287-49c9-a737-cfe7a8a2615a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_driver_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8186">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8186">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8187">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8187">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8188">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными делегаторами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8188">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8189">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8189">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8190">восемь или девять цифр с необязательными делегаторами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8190">eight or nine digits with optional delimiters</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8191">две или три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8191">two or three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8192">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8192">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8193">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8193">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8194">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8194">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8195">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8195">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8196">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8196">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8197">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8197">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8198">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8198">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8199">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8199">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8200">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8200">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8201">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8201">A keyword from Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8202">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8202">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8203">Функция Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8203">The function Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- New Zealand Inland Revenue Number -->
      <Entity id="dd0fe2bc-7bcf-455f-bac1-83b1e3eb25fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8204">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8204">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8205">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8205">Keyword_new_zealand_inland_revenue_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8206">ird no.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8206">ird no.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8207">ird no #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8207">ird no#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8208">nz ird</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8208">nz ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8209">новая Зеландия ird</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8209">new zealand ird</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8210">ird number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8210">ird number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8211">inland revenue number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8211">inland revenue number</span></span>


## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8212">Министерство здравоохранения Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8212">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8213">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8213">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8214">три буквы, пробел (необязательно) и четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8214">three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8215">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8215">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8216">три буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), кроме "I" и "O"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8216">three letters (not case sensitive) except 'I' and 'O'</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8217">пробел (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8217">a space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8218">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8218">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8219">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8219">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8220">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8220">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8221">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8221">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8222">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8222">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8223">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8223">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8224">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_nz_terms;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8224">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8225">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8225">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8226">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8226">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8227">функция Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8227">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8228">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8228">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
    <Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
       </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_nz_terms"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8230">Keyword_nz_terms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8230">Keyword_nz_terms</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8239">National Health Index No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8239">National Health Index No.</span></span>

## <a name="new-zealand-social-welfare-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8242">Номер социальных сетей Новой Зеландии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8242">New Zealand social welfare number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8243">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8243">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8244">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8244">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8245">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8245">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8246">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8246">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8247">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8247">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8248">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8248">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8249">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8249">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8250">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8250">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8251">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8251">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8252">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8252">nine digits</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8253">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8253">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8254">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8254">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8255">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8255">three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8256">необязательный дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8256">an optional hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8257">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8257">three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8258">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8258">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8259">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8259">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8260">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8260">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8261">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8261">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8262">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8262">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8263">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8263">A keyword from Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8264">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8264">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8265">Функция Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8265">The function Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Newzealand Social Welfare Number -->
      <Entity id="20f3c48d-4ac1-4cd2-86bd-34ecc1826e9d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_newzealand_social_welfare_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8266">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8266">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8267">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8267">Keyword_new_zealand_social_welfare_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8268">социальные сети #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8268">social welfare #</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8269">социальные сети #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8269">social welfare#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8270">social welfare No.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8270">social welfare No.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8271">номер социальных сетей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8271">social welfare number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8272">swn #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8272">swn#</span></span>

   
## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8273">Идентификационный номер для Норвегии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8273">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8274">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8274">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8275">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8275">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8276">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8276">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8277">11 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8277">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8278">шесть цифр в формате ДДММАЙ, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8278">six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8279">трехзначный индивидуальный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8279">three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8280">две контрольные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8280">two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8281">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8281">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8282">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8282">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8283">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8283">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8284">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8284">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8285">функция Func_norway_id_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8285">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8286">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_norway_id_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8286">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8287">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8287">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8288">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8288">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8289">функция Func_norway_id_numbe находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8289">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8290">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8290">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8295">ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8295">ID Number</span></span>

## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8299">Единый многонамерный идентификационный номер для Филиппин</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8299">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8300">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8300">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8301">12 цифр, разделенных дефисами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8301">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8302">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8302">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8303">12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8303">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8304">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8304">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8305">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8305">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8306">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8306">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8307">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8307">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8308">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8308">one digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8309">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8309">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8310">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8310">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8311">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8311">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8312">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8312">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8313">регулярное выражение Regex_philippines_unified_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8313">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8314">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_philippines_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8314">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8315">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8315">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_philippines_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8316">Keyword_philippines_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8316">Keyword_philippines_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8317">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8317">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8318">UMID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8318">UMID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8319">Identity Card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8319">Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8320">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8320">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span></span>

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8321">Номер водительского удостоверения для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8321">Poland driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8322">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8322">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8323">14 цифр, содержащих 2 косые черты</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8323">14 digits containing 2 forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8324">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8324">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8325">14 цифр и 2 косой черты:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8325">14 digits and 2 forward slashes:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8326">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8326">five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8327">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8327">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8328">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8328">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8329">косая черта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8329">a forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8330">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8330">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8331">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8331">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8332">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8332">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8333">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8333">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8334">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8334">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8335">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8335">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8336">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8336">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Poland Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="24d51f99-ee9e-4060-a077-cae58cab1ee4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8460">Удостоверение личности для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8460">Poland identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8461">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8461">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8462">три буквы и шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8462">three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8463">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8463">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8464">три буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), за которыми следуют шесть цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8464">three letters (not case sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8465">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8465">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8466">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8466">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8467">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8467">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8468">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8468">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8469">функция Func_polish_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8469">The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8470">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8470">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8471">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8471">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8472">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8472">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8473">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8473">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8474">Dowód osobisty</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8474">Dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8475">Numer dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8475">Numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8476">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8476">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8477">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8477">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8478">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8478">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8479">Dowód Tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8479">Dowód Tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8480">dow.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8480">dow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8481">os.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8481">os.</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8482">Национальный ИД для Польша (PESEL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8482">Poland national ID (PESEL)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8483">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8483">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8484">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8484">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8485">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8485">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8486">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения в формате YYMMDD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8486">6 digits representing date of birth in the format YYMMDD</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8487">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8487">4 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8488">1 контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8488">1 check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8489">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8489">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8490">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8490">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8491">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8491">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8492">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8492">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8493">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8493">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8494">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_pesel_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8494">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8495">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8495">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8496">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8496">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8497">функция Func_pesel_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8497">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8498">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8498">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->
      <Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8510">Номер паспорта гражданина Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8510">Poland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8511">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ес и доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8511">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8512">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8512">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8513">две буквы и семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8513">two letters and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8514">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8514">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8515">Две буквы (без учета регистра), за которыми следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8515">Two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8516">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8516">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8517">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8517">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8518">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8518">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8519">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8519">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8520">функция Func_polish_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8520">The function Func_polish_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8521">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8521">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8522">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8522">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Passport Number -->
<Entity id="03937FB5-D2B6-4487-B61F-0F8BFF7C3517" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
</Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8523">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8523">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8524">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8524">Keyword_poland_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8525">Numer paszportu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8525">Numer paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8526">Nr.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8526">Nr.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8527">Paszportu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8527">Paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8528">Paszport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8528">Paszport</span></span>

## <a name="poland-regon-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8529">Номер REGON для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8529">Poland REGON number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8530">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8530">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8531">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8531">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8532">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8532">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8533">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8533">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8534">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8534">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8535">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8535">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8536">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8536">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8537">девятизначный или 14-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8537">nine digit or 14 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8538">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8538">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8539">девятизначное или 14-значное число:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8539">nine digit or 14-digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8540">девять цифр или</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8540">nine digits or</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8541">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8541">nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8542">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8542">hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8543">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8543">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8544">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8544">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8545">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8545">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8546">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8546">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8547">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8547">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8548">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8548">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8549">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_polish_regon_number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8549">A keyword from Keywords_polish_regon_number is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8550">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8550">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8551">Функция Func_polish_regon_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8551">The function Func_polish_regon_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Polish REGON Number  -->
      <Entity id="fc87b421-f437-4f8b-b739-29a735ead0d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_regon_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="poland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8568">Налоговый идентификационный номер для Польша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8568">Poland tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8569">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8569">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8570">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8570">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8571">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8571">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8572">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8572">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8573">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8573">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8574">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8574">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8575">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8575">Format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8577">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8577">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8578">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8578">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8579">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8579">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8580">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8580">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8581">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8581">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8582">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8582">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8583">Функция находит  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8583">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <Entity id="1ff28b4d-40f2-49e9-b677-9606a88e2bca" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">

          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-citizen-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8614">Номер карты гражданина Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8614">Portugal citizen card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8615">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8615">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8616">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8616">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8617">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8617">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8618">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8618">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8619">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8619">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8620">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8620">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8621">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8621">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8622">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8622">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8623">регулярное выражение Regex_portugal_citizen_card находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8623">The regular expression Regex_portugal_citizen_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8624">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_portugal_citizen_card.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8624">A keyword from Keyword_portugal_citizen_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Portugal Citizen Card Number -->
<Entity id="91a7ece2-add4-4986-9a15-c84544d81ecd" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_citizen_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_portugal_citizen_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8644">Номер водительского удостоверения для Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8644">Portugal driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8645">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8645">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8646">два шаблона: две буквы, за которыми следуют 5–8 цифр со специальными символами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8646">two patterns - two letters followed by 5-8 digits with special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8647">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8647">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8648">Шаблон 1: две буквы, за которыми следуют 5/6 со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8648">Pattern 1: Two letters followed by 5/6 with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8649">Две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8649">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8650">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8650">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8651">Пять или шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8651">Five or Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8652">Пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8652">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8653">Одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8653">One digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8654">Шаблон 2: одна буква, за которой следуют 6/8 цифр со специальными символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8654">Pattern 2: One letter followed by 6/8 digits with special characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8655">Одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8655">One letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8656">дефис;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8656">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8657">Шесть или восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8657">Six or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8658">Пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8658">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8659">одна цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8659">One digit</span></span>

    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8660">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8660">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8661">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8661">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8662">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8662">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8663">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8663">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8664">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8664">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8665">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8665">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="977f1e5a-2c33-4bcc-b516-95bb275cff23" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8797">Номер паспорта гражданина Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8797">Portugal passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8798">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8798">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8799">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8799">one letter followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8800">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8800">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8801">одна буква, за которой следуют шесть цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8801">one letter followed by six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8802">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8802">one letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8803">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8803">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8804">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8804">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8805">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8805">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8806">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8806">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8807">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8807">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8808">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8808">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8809">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8809">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8810">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8810">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8811">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8811">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8812">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8812">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8813">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8813">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="080a52fd-a7bc-431e-b54d-51f08f59db11" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8840">Идентификационный номер налога для Португалии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8840">Portugal tax identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8841">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8841">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8842">девять цифр с необязательными пробелами</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8842">nine digits with optional spaces</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8843">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8843">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8844">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8844">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8845">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8845">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8846">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8846">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8847">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8847">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8848">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8848">3 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8849">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8849">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8850">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8850">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8851">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8851">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8852">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8852">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8853">Функция находит  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8853">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8854">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8854">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8855">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8855">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8856">Функция находит  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8856">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Portugal Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="65372402-3131-4f1e-9983-4439841d1f15" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
