## <a name="romania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8881">Номер водительского удостоверения в Румынии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8881">Romania driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8882">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8882">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8883">один символ, за которым следует восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8883">one character followed by eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8884">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8884">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8885">один символ, за которым следует восемь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8885">one character followed by eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8886">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8886">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8887">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8887">eight digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8888">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8888">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8889">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8889">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8890">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8890">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8891">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8891">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8892">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8892">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-8893">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-8893">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="b5511ace-2fd8-4ae4-b6fc-c7c6e4689e3c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-personal-numeric-code-cnp"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9021">Личный числовой код Румынии (CNP)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9021">Romania personal numeric code (CNP)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9022">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9022">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9023">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9023">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9024">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9024">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9025">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9025">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9026">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9026">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9027">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9027">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9028">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9028">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9029">13 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9029">13 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9030">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9030">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9031">1 цифра от 1 до 9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9031">1 digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9032">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9032">6 digits representing date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9033">2 цифры, которые могут быть 01–52 или 99</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9033">2 digits which can be 01-52 or 99</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9034">4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9034">4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9035">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9035">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9036">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9036">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9037">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9037">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9038">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9038">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9039">Функция находит  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9039">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9040">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9040">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9041">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9041">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9042">Функция находит  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9042">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Personal Numerical Code (CNP) -->
      <Entity id="eb5fa399-fe28-4c67-8188-d63a616ed89c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9093">Номер паспорта гражданина Румынии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9093">Romania passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9094">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9094">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9095">восемь или девять цифр без пробелов и делегаторов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9095">eight or nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9096">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9096">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9097">восемь или девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9097">eight or nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9098">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9098">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9099">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9099">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9100">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9100">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9101">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9101">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9102">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9102">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9103">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9103">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9104">Регулярное выражение находит дату в формате `Regex_romania_eu_passport_date` DD MMM/MMM YY (пример: 01 FEB/FEB 10) или находится ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9104">The regular expression `Regex_romania_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD MMM/MMM YY (Example- 01 FEB/FEB 10) or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9105">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9105">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9106">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9106">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9107">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9107">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Romania Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="5d31b90c-7fe2-4a76-a14b-767b8fd19d6c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="russia-passport-number-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9125">Внутренний номер паспорта гражданина России</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9125">Russia passport number domestic</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9126">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9126">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9127">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9127">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9128">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9128">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9129">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9129">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9130">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9130">records management</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9132">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9132">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9133">десятизначный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9133">ten digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9134">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9134">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9135">десятизначный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9135">ten digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9136">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9136">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9137">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9137">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9138">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9138">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9139">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9139">an optional space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9140">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9140">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9141">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9141">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9142">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9142">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9143">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9143">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9144">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9144">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9145">Regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9145">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9146">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9146">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number Domestic -->
      <Entity id="76ec2f5d-cedb-48e1-8070-1998794af445" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_Domestic" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9156">id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9156">паспорт id</span></span>

## <a name="russia-passport-number-international"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9163">Международный номер паспорта гражданина России</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9163">Russia passport number international</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9164">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9164">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9165">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9165">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9166">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9166">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9167">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9167">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9168">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9168">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9169">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9169">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9170">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9170">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9171">девятизначный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9171">nine digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9172">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9172">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9173">девятизначный номер:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9173">nine digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9174">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9174">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9175">необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9175">an optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9176">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9176">seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9177">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9177">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9178">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9178">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9179">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9179">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9180">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9180">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9181">Regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9181">The regex Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9182">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9182">A keyword from Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Russian Passport Number International -->
      <Entity id="ac5f4878-75e4-4b82-af2d-02e13ea9f411" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Russian_Passport_Number_International" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Russian_Passport_Number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="saudi-arabia-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9199">Национальный идентификатор для Саудовской Аравии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9199">Saudi Arabia National ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9200">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9200">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9201">десять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9201">ten digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9202">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9202">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9203">десять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9203">ten consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9204">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9204">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9205">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9205">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9206">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9206">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9207">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9207">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9208">регулярное выражение Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9208">The regular expression Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9209">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9209">A keyword from Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Saudi Arabia National ID -->
<Entity id="8c5a0ba8-404a-41a3-8871-746aa21ee6c0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="singapore-national-registration-identity-card-nric-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9216">Номер удостоверения личности для национальной регистрации Сингапура (NRIC)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9216">Singapore national registration identity card (NRIC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9217">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9217">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9218">девять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9218">nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9219">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9219">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9220">девять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9220">nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9221">буква "F", "G", "S" или "T" (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9221">the letter "F", "G", "S", or "T" (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9222">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9222">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9223">алфавитная проверочные цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9223">an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9224">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9224">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9225">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9225">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9226">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9226">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9227">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9227">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9228">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9228">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9229">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_singapore_nric;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9229">A keyword from Keyword_singapore_nric is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9230">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9230">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9231">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9231">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9232">регулярное выражение Regex_singapore_nric находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9232">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9233">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9233">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Singapore National Registration Identity Card (NRIC) Number -->
<Entity id="cead390a-dd83-4856-9751-fb6dc98c34da" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9244">Номер водительского удостоверения для Словакии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9244">Slovakia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9245">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9245">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9246">один символ, за которым следует семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9246">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9247">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9247">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9248">один символ, за которым следует семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9248">one character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9249">одна буква (без чувствительность к букве) или цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9249">one letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9250">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9250">seven digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9251">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9251">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9252">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9252">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9253">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9253">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9254">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9254">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9255">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9255">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9256">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9256">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="14240c22-b6de-4ce5-a90b-137f74252513" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-personal-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9382">Персональный номер для Словакии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9382">Slovakia personal number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9383">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9383">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9384">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9384">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9385">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9385">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9386">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9386">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9387">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9387">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9388">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9388">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9389">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9389">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9390">девять или десять цифр, содержащих необязательные знаки backslash</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9390">nine or ten digits containing optional backslash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9391">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9391">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9392">6 цифр, представляющих дату рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9392">6 digits representing date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9393">необязательная косая черта (/)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9393">optional slash (/)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9394">3 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9394">3 digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9395">1 дополнительная проверотельная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9395">1 optional check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9396">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9396">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9397">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9397">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9398">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9398">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9399">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9399">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9400">Функция находит  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9400">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9401">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9401">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9402">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9402">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9403">Функция находит  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9403">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Personal Number -->
      <Entity id="951c26b7-3b35-4f73-924b-15dd599cb9ab" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
    </Version>
```

## <a name="slovakia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9450">Номер паспорта гражданина Словакии</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9450">Slovakia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9451">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9451">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9452">одна цифра или буква, за которой следуют семь цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9452">one digit or letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9453">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9453">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9454">одна цифра или буква (без чувствительность к букве), за которой следуют семь цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9454">one digit or letter (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9455">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9455">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9456">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9456">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9457">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9457">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9458">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9458">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9459">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9459">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9460">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9460">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9461">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9461">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9462">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9462">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9463">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9463">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9464">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9464">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovakia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="238e1f08-d80e-4793-af33-9b57918335b7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9486">Номер водительского удостоверения для Словении</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9486">Slovenia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9487">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9487">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9488">девять цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9488">nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9489">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9489">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9490">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9490">nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9491">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9491">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9492">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9492">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9493">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9493">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9494">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9494">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9495">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9495">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9496">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9496">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5bc089a-f2ee-433d-a6b1-5c253051d6f2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-unique-master-citizen-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9623">Уникальный номер гражданина Словении</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9623">Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9624">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9624">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9625">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9625">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9626">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9626">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9627">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9627">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9628">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9628">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9629">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9629">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9630">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9630">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9631">13 цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9631">13 digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9632">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9632">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9633">13 цифр в указанном шаблоне:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9633">13 digits in the specified pattern:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9634">семь цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (DDMMLLL), где "LLL" соответствует последним трем цифрам года рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9634">seven digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMLLL) where "LLL" corresponds to the last three digits of the birth year</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9635">две цифры, соответствующие области рождения "50"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9635">two digits that correspond to the area of birth "50"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9636">три цифры, соответствующие комбинации пола и серийного номера для людей, которые были в один день (000–499 для детей и 500–999 для детей)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9636">three digits that correspond to a combination of gender and serial number for persons born on the same day (000-499 for male and 500-999 for female)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9637">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9637">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9638">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9638">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9639">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9639">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9640">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9640">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9641">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9641">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9642">Функция находит  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9642">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9643">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9643">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9644">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9644">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9645">Функция находит  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9645">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Unique Master Citizen Number -->
      <Entity id="68948b27-803d-41e4-adf1-13e05eb541bb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9673">Номер паспорта гражданина Словении</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9673">Slovenia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9674">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9674">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9675">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр без пробелов или седиметров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9675">two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9676">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9676">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9677">две буквы, за которыми следуют семь цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9677">two letters followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9678">буква "P"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9678">the letter "P"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9679">одна буква в верхнем регистре</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9679">one uppercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9680">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9680">seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9681">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9681">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9682">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9682">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9683">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9683">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9684">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9684">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9685">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9685">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9686">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9686">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9687">Регулярное выражение `Regex_eu_passport_date1` находит дату в формате ДД.ММ.YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9687">The regular expression `Regex_eu_passport_date1` finds date in the format DD.MM.YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9688">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9688">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9689">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9689">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9690">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9690">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="235b7976-7bbe-4df5-bb40-08678e749d1a" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_eu_passport_date1" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9691">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9691">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9692">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9692">Keywords_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9695">passportid</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9695">passportid</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9698">passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9698">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9699">passportnumber</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9699">passportnumber</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9700">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9700">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9701">passportnumbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9701">passportnumbers</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9702">passport numbers</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9702">passport numbers</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9703">Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9703">Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9704">гtevilka potnega lista</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9704">številka potnega lista</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9705">potek veljavnosti</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9705">potek veljavnosti</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9706">список potni #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9706">potni list#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9707">datum rojstva</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9707">datum rojstva</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9708">список potni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9708">potni list</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9709">гtevilke potnih listov</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9709">številke potnih listov</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_passport_date"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9710">Keywords_eu_passport_date</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9710">Keywords_eu_passport_date</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9711">дата проблемы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9711">date of issue</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9712">дата окончания срока действия</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9712">date of expiry</span></span>


## <a name="slovenia-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9713">Идентификационный номер налога для Словении</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9713">Slovenia tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9714">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9714">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9715">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9715">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9716">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9716">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9717">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9717">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9718">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9718">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9719">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9719">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9720">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9720">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9721">восемь цифр без пробелов или делегировок</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9721">eight digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9722">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9722">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9723">одна цифра от 1 до 9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9723">one digit from 1-9</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9724">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9724">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9725">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9725">one check digit</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9726">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9726">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9727">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9727">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9728">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9728">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9729">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9729">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9730">Функция находит  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9730">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9731">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9731">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9732">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9732">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9733">Функция находит  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9733">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Slovenia Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="e47b071e-c352-4d70-8241-8c215ad65505" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="south-africa-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9757">Идентификационный номер для Южной Африки</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9757">South Africa identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9758">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9758">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9759">13 цифр, которые могут содержать пробелы.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9759">13 digits that may contain spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9760">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9760">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9761">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9761">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9762">шесть цифр в формате YYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9762">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9763">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9763">four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9764">индикатор гражданства из одной цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9764">a single-digit citizenship indicator</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9765">цифра "8" или "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9765">the digit "8" or "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9766">одна цифра, которая является цифрой контрольной суммы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9766">one digit which is a checksum digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9767">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9767">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9768">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9768">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9769">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9769">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9770">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9770">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9771">функция Func_south_africa_identification_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9771">The function Func_south_africa_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9772">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_south_africa_identification_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9772">A keyword from Keyword_south_africa_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9773">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9773">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Africa Identification Number -->
<Entity id="e2adf7cb-8ea6-4048-a2ed-d89eb65f2780" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_africa_identification_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_africa_identification_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9774">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9774">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9776">Identity card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9776">Identity card</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9777">Идентификатор</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9777">ID</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9778">Идентификация</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9778">Identification</span></span> 
   
## <a name="south-korea-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9779">Регистрационный номер резидента Южной Кореи</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9779">South Korea resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9780">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9780">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9781">13 цифр, содержащих дефис.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9781">13 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9782">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9782">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9783">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9783">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9784">шесть цифр в формате YYMMDD, которые являются датой рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9784">six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9785">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9785">a hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9786">одна цифра, определяемая возрастом и полом</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9786">one digit determined by the century and gender</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9787">четырехзначный код региона рождения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9787">four-digit region-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9788">одна цифра, используемая для различения людей, для которых предыдущие числа идентичны</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9788">one digit used to differentiate people for whom the preceding numbers are identical</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9789">контрольная цифра.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9789">a check digit.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9790">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9790">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9791">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9791">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9792">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9792">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9793">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9793">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9794">функция Func_south_korea_resident_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9794">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9795">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_south_korea_resident_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9795">A keyword from Keyword_south_korea_resident_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9796">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9796">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9797">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9797">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9798">функция Func_south_korea_resident_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9798">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9799">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9799">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Korea Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="5b802e18-ba80-44c4-bc83-bf2ad36ae36a" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9800">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9800">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_south_korea_resident_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9801">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9801">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9802">National ID card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9802">National ID card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9803">Citizen's Registration Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9803">Citizen's Registration Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9804">Jumin deungnok beonho</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9804">Jumin deungnok beonho</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9805">RRN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9805">RRN</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9806">주민등록번호</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9806">주민등록번호</span></span>

## <a name="spain-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9807">Номер водительского удостоверения для Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9807">Spain driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9808">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9808">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9809">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9809">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9810">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9810">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9811">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9811">eight digits followed by one character:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9812">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9812">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9813">одна цифра или буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9813">one digit or letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9814">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9814">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9815">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9815">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9816">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9816">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9817">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9817">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9818">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` находит `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9818">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9819">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9819">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9820">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9820">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9821">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` находит `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9821">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="d5a82922-b501-4f40-8868-341321146aa2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9822">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9822">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_eu_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9823">Keywords_eu_driver s_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9823">Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9824">driverlic</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9824">driverlic</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9825">driverlics</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9825">driverlics</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9826">driverlicense</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9826">driverlicense</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9827">driverlicenses</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9827">driverlicenses</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9828">driverlicence</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9828">driverlicence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9829">driverlicences</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9829">driverlicences</span></span>
