### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9962">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9962">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9963">восемь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9963">eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9964">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9964">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9965">семь цифр, за которыми следует один символ</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9965">seven digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9966">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9966">eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9967">Необязательный пробел или дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9967">An optional space or hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9968">одна контрольная буква (без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9968">one check letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9969">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9969">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9970">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9970">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9971">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9971">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9972">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9972">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9973">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` находит `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9973">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9974">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9974">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9975">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9975">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-9976">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` находит `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-9976">The function  `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

    
```xml
      <!-- Spain DNI -->
      <Entity id="8e6251b9-47b4-40e8-a42b-0f80876be192" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_foreigner" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10000">Номер паспорта гражданина Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10000">Spain passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10001">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10001">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10002">сочетание букв и чисел из восьми или девяти символов без пробелов или делений.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10002">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10003">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10003">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10004">восьми- или девяти символьное сочетание букв и чисел:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10004">an eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10005">две цифры или буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10005">two digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10006">одна цифра или буква (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10006">one digit or letter (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10007">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10007">six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10008">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10008">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10009">Неприменимо</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10009">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10010">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10010">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10011">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10011">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10012">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10012">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10013">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10013">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10014">Регулярное выражение `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` находит дату в формате ДД-ММ-YYYY или ключевое слово `Keywords_eu_passport_date` из</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10014">The regular expression `Regex_spain_eu_passport_date` finds date in the format DD-MM-YYYY or a keyword from `Keywords_eu_passport_date` is found</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10015">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10015">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10016">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10016">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10017">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` из или `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10017">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_passport_number` or `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Passport Number -->
      <Entity id="d17a57de-9fa5-4e9f-85d3-85c26d89686e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_date" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_date" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_passport_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10046">Номер социального обеспечения в Испании (SSN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10046">Spain social security number (SSN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10047">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10047">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10048">11–12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10048">11-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10049">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10049">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10050">11–12 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10050">11-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10051">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10051">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10052">косая черта (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10052">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10053">семь-восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10053">seven to eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10054">косая черта (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10054">a forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10055">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10055">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10056">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10056">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10057">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10057">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10058">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10058">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10059">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10059">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10060">функция Func_spanish_social_security_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10060">The function Func_spanish_social_security_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10061">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10061">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Spain SSN -->
<Entity id="5df987c0-8eae-4bce-ace7-b316347f3070" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_spanish_social_security_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10062">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10062">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10063">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10063">None</span></span>

## <a name="spain-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10064">Идентификационный номер налога для Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10064">Spain tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10065">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10065">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10066">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10066">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10067">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10067">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10068">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10068">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10069">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10069">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10070">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10070">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10071">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10071">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10072">семь или восемь цифр и одна или две буквы в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10072">seven or eight digits and one or two letters in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10073">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10073">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10074">Испанские персональные лица с национальные удостоверения личности для Испании:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10074">Spanish Natural Persons with a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10075">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10075">eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10076">одна буква в верхнем регистре (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10076">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10077">Нерезиденты без национального удостоверения личности для Испании</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10077">Non-resident Spaniards without a Spain National Identity Card</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10078">одна буква в верхнем регистре "L" (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10078">one uppercase letter "L" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10079">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10079">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10080">одна буква в верхнем регистре (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10080">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10081">Resident Resident Residents under the age of 14 years without a Spain National Identity Card :</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10081">Resident Spaniards under the age of 14 years without a Spain National Identity Card :</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10082">одна буква в верхнем регистре "K" (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10082">one uppercase letter"K" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10083">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10083">seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10084">одна буква в верхнем регистре (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10084">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10085">Подмена идентификационных номеров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10085">Foreigners with a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10086">одна буква в верхнем регистре, которая имеет буквы "X", "Y" или "Z" (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10086">one uppercase letter that is "X", "Y", or "Z" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10087">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10087">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10088">одна буква в верхнем регистре (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10088">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10089">Подмена без идентификации по идентификационным номерам</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10089">Foreigners without a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10090">одна буква в верхнем регистре с буквой "M" (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10090">one uppercase letter that is "M" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10091">семь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10091">seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10092">одна буква в верхнем регистре (с чувствительностью к регистру)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10092">one uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10093">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10093">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10094">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10094">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10095">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10095">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10096">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10096">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10097">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` находит `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10097">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10098">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10098">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10099">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10099">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10100">Функция или  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` находит `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10100">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` or `Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Spain Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="10f0d113-b0e1-47dc-872a-a4f45b9376a3" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_DL_and_NI_number_citizen" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sql-server-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10131">SQL Server подключения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10131">SQL Server connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10132">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10132">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10133">Строка "User Id", "User ID", "uid" или "UserId", за которой следуют символы и строки, описанные в шаблоне ниже.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10133">The string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10134">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10134">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10135">строка "User Id", "User ID", "uid" или "UserId"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10135">the string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10136">любое сочетание от 1 до 200 букв нижнего или верхнего регистра, цифр, символов, специальных символов или пробелов</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10136">any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10137">строка "Password" или "pwd", где "pwd" не предшествует строчная буква</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10137">the string "Password" or "pwd" where "pwd" is not preceded by a lowercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10138">знак равного (=)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10138">an equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10139">любой символ, который не является знаком доллара ($), символом процента (%), больше символа (>), в символе (@), кавычках ("), точка с зазнаковкой (;), левая скобка ([) или левая скобка ({)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10139">any character that is not a dollar sign ($), percent symbol (%), greater than symbol (>), at symbol (@), quotation mark ("), semicolon (;), left brace([), or left bracket ({)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10140">любое сочетание 7–128 символов, которые не являются пустяковой (;) косой черты (/) или кавычка ()</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10140">any combination of 7-128 characters that are not a semicolon (;), forward slash (/), or quotation mark (")</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10141">точка с зачетом (;) или кавычка (")</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10141">a semicolon (;) or quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10142">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10142">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10143">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10143">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10144">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10144">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10145">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10145">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10146">Регулярное выражение CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10146">The regular expression CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10147">Ключевое слово из CEP_GlobalFilter **не** найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10147">A keyword from CEP_GlobalFilter is **not** found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10148">Регулярное выражение CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder **не находит** содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10148">The regular expression CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10149">Регулярное выражение CEP_CommonExampleKeywords **не находит** содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10149">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```sql
<!---SQL Server Connection String>
<Entity id="e76b6205-d3cb-46f2-bd63-c90153f2f97d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_GlobalFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10150">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10150">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_globalfilter"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10151">CEP_GlobalFilter</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10151">CEP_GlobalFilter</span></span>

## <a name="sweden-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10177">Номер водительского удостоверения для Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10177">Sweden driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10178">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10178">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10179">десять цифр, содержащих дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10179">ten digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10180">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10180">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10181">десять цифр, содержащих дефис:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10181">ten digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10182">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10182">six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10183">дефис</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10183">a hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10184">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10184">four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10185">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10185">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10186">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10186">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10187">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10187">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10188">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10188">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10189">Регулярное выражение  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10189">The regular expression  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10190">Ключевое слово  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` из или `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` найдено.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10190">A keyword from  `Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number` or `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Driver's License Number -->
      <Entity id="70088720-90dd-47f5-805e-5525f3567391" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_eu_driver's_license_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10323">Национальный ИД Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10323">Sweden national ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10324">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10324">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10325">10 или 12 цифр и необязательный седиметр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10325">ten or 12 digits and an optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10326">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10326">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10327">10 или 12 цифр и необязательный делегатор:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10327">ten or 12 digits and an optional delimiter:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10328">две цифры (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10328">two digits (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10329">Шесть цифр в формате даты ГГММДД.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10329">Six digits in date format YYMMDD</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10330">либо "-" или "+" (необязательно)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10330">delimiter of "-" or "+" (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10331">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10331">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10332">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10332">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10333">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10333">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10334">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10334">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10335">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10335">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10336">Функция находит `Func_swedish_national_identifier` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10336">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10337">Найдено ключевое `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` слово</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10337">A keyword from `Keywords_swedish_national_identifier` is found</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10338">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10338">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10339">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10339">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10340">Функция находит `Func_swedish_national_identifier` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10340">The function `Func_swedish_national_identifier` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10341">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10341">The checksum passes.</span></span>


```xml
    <!-- Sweden National ID -->
    <Entity id="f69aaf40-79be-4fac-8f05-fd1910d272c8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
        <Match idRef="Keywords_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10360">Номер паспорта гражданина Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10360">Sweden passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10361">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ес и доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10361">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10362">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10362">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10363">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10363">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10364">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10364">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10365">восемь последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10365">eight consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10366">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10366">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10367">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10367">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10368">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10368">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10369">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10369">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10370">регулярное выражение Regex_sweden_passport_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10370">the regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10371">Верно одно из следующих:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10371">one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10372">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10372">a keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10373">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_sweden_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10373">a keyword from Keyword_sweden_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Sweden Passport Number -->
<Entity id="ba4e7456-55a9-4d89-9140-c33673553526" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10374">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10374">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10376">visa requirements</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10376">visa requirements</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10378">Schengen visas</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10378">Schengen visas</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10379">Schengen visa</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10379">Schengen visa</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10380">Visa Processing</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10380">Visa Processing</span></span>

## <a name="sweden-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10404">Идентификационный номер налога для Швеции</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10404">Sweden tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10405">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10405">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10406">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10406">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10407">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10407">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10408">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10408">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10409">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10409">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10410">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10410">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10411">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10411">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10412">десять цифр и символ в указанном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10412">ten digits and a symbol in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10413">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10413">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10414">десять цифр и символ:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10414">ten digits and a symbol:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10415">шесть цифр, соответствующих дате рождения (YYMMDD)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10415">six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10416">знак "плюс" или "минус"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10416">a plus sign or minus sign</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10417">три цифры, которые делают идентификационный номер уникальным, где:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10417">three digits that make the identification number unique where:</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10418">для номеров, выдавшихся до 1990 г., седьмая и восьмая цифры определяют округ рождения или инородных людей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10418">for numbers issued before 1990, the seventh and eighth digit identify the county of birth or foreign-born people</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10419">цифра в девятом положении указывает пол по нечетным для самцов или даже для женщина</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10419">the digit in the ninth position indicates gender by either odd for male or even for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10420">одна контрольная цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10420">one check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10421">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10421">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10422">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10422">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10423">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10423">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10424">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10424">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10425">Функция находит  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10425">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10426">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10426">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10427">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10427">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10428">Функция находит  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10428">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- Sweden Tax Identification Number -->
      <Entity id="139acba0-a5bc-4fbb-876d-f7a493ae8a40" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_telephone_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_mobile_number" />
          </Any>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="swift-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10454">Код SWIFT</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10454">SWIFT code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10455">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10455">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10456">четыре буквы, за которыми следуют от 5 до 31 буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10456">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10457">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10457">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10458">четыре буквы, за которыми следуют 5–31 буква или цифры:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10458">four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10459">4-буква банковского кода (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10459">four-letter bank code (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10460">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10460">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10461">4–28 букв или цифр (основной номер банковского счета, BBAN)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10461">4-28 letters or digits (the Basic Bank Account Number (BBAN))</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10462">дополнительное пространство</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10462">an optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10463">от одной до трех букв или цифр (оставшаяся часть BBAN);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10463">one to three letters or digits (remainder of the BBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10464">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10464">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10465">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10465">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10466">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10466">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10467">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10467">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10468">регулярное выражение Regex_swift находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10468">The regular expression Regex_swift finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10469">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_swift.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10469">A keyword from Keyword_swift is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="cb2ab58c-9cb8-4c81-baf8-a4e106791df4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_swift" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_swift" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="switzerland-ssn-ahv-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10506">Номер АЧЧ для швейцарии SSN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10506">Switzerland SSN AHV number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10507">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10507">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10508">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10508">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10509">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10509">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10510">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10510">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10511">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10511">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10512">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10512">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10513">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10513">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10514">13-значный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10514">13 digit number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10515">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10515">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10516">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10516">13 digit number:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10517">три цифры — 756</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10517">three digits - 756</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10518">необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10518">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10519">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10519">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10520">необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10520">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10521">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10521">four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10522">необязательная точка</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10522">an optional dot</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10523">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10523">two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10524">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10524">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10525">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10525">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10526">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10526">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10527">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10527">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10528">Функция Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10528">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10529">Находится ключевое слово из Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10529">A keyword from Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10530">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10530">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10531">Функция Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10531">The function Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Swiss SSN AHV Number -->
      <Entity id="277cfa4b-6eaa-4a1b-9492-099dec849971" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_swiss_social_security_number_ahv" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="taiwan-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10552">Национальный идентификационный номер для Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10552">Taiwan national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10553">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10553">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10554">одна буква (на английском языке), за которой следуют девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10554">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10555">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10555">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10556">одна буква (на английском языке), за которой следуют девять цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10556">one letter (in English) followed by nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10557">одна буква (на английском языке без чувствительность к букве)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10557">one letter (in English, not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10558">цифра "1" или "2"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10558">the digit "1" or "2"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10559">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10559">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10560">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10560">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10561">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10561">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10562">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10562">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10563">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10563">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10564">функция Func_taiwanese_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10564">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10565">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwanese_national_id;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10565">A keyword from Keyword_taiwanese_national_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10566">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10566">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10567">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10567">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10568">функция Func_taiwanese_national_id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10568">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10569">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10569">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwanese National ID -->
<Entity id="4C7BFC34-8DD1-421D-8FB7-6C6182C2AF03" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwanese_national_id" />
      </Pattern>
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
         <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
       </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10576">身分證字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10576">身分證字號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10577">身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10577">身分證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10578">身分證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10578">身分證號碼</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10579">身份證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10579">身份證號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10580">身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10580">身分證統一編號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10581">國民身分證統一編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10581">國民身分證統一編號</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10582">簽名</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10582">簽名</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10583">蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10583">蓋章</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10584">簽名或蓋章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10584">簽名或蓋章</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10585">簽章</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10585">簽章</span></span>   
   
## <a name="taiwan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10586">Номер паспорта гражданина Тайваня</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10586">Taiwan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10587">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10587">Format</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10588">биометрический номер паспорта: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10588">biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10589">Номер не биометрического паспорта: девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10589">non-biometric passport number: nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10590">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10590">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10591">биометрический номер паспорта:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10591">biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10592">символ "3"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10592">the character "3"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10593">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10593">eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10594">не биометрический номер паспорта:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10594">non-biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10595">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10595">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10596">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10596">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10597">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10597">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10598">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10598">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10599">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10599">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10600">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10600">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10601">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10601">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="e7251cb4-4c2c-41df-963e-924eb3dae04a" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_passport"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_passport"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10606">Passport no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10606">Passport no</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10607">Passport Num</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10607">Passport Num</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10608">Passport #</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10608">Passport #</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10609">护照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10609">护照</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10610">中華民國護照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10610">中華民國護照</span></span>
