## <a name="taiwan-resident-certificate-arctarc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10612">Номер сертификата резидента Тайваня (ARC/TARC)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10612">Taiwan resident certificate (ARC/TARC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10613">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10613">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10614">десять букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10614">ten letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10615">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10615">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10616">десять букв и цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10616">ten letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10617">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10617">two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10618">восемь цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10618">eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10619">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10619">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10620">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10620">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10621">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10621">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10622">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10622">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10623">регулярное выражение Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10623">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10624">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10624">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Resident Certificate (ARC/TARC) -->
<Entity id="48269fec-05ea-46ea-b326-f5623a58c6e9" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10625">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10625">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10626">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10626">Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10627">Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10627">Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10628">Resident Cert</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10628">Resident Cert</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10629">Resident Cert.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10629">Resident Cert.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10630">Identification card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10630">Identification card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10631">Alien Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10631">Alien Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10632">ARC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10632">ARC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10633">Taiwan Area Resident Certificate</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10633">Taiwan Area Resident Certificate</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10634">TARC</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10634">TARC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10635">居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10635">居留證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10636">外僑居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10636">外僑居留證</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10637">台灣地區居留證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10637">台灣地區居留證</span></span> 

## <a name="thai-population-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10638">Идентификационный код для тайских пользователей</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10638">Thai population identification code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10639">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10639">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10640">13 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10640">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10641">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10641">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10642">13 цифр:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10642">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10643">первая цифра не нуль или девять</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10643">first digit is not zero  or nine</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10644">12 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10644">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10645">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10645">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10646">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10646">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10647">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10647">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10648">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10648">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10649">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10649">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10650">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10650">A keyword from Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10651">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10651">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10652">Функция Func_Thai_Citizen_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10652">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Thai Citizen ID -->
-<Entity id="44ca9e86-ead7-4c5d-884a-e2eaa401515e" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10653">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10653">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_thai_citizen_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10654">Keyword_thai_citizen_Id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10654">Keyword_thai_citizen_Id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10655">ID Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10655">ID Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10656">Идентификационный номер</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10656">Identification Number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10657">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10657">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10658">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10658">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10659">บัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10659">บัตรประชาชน</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10660">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10660">รหัสบัตรประชาชน</span></span>
  
## <a name="turkish-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10661">Идентификационный номер гражданина Турецкий</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10661">Turkish national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10662">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10662">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10663">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10663">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10664">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10664">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10665">11 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10665">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10666">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10666">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10667">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10667">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10668">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10668">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10669">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10669">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10670">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10670">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10671">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Turkish_National_Id.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10671">A keyword from Keyword_Turkish_National_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10672">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10672">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10673">Функция Func_Turkish_National_Id находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10673">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Turkish National Identity -->
-<Entity id="fb621f20-3876-4cfc-acec-8c8e73ca32c7" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10674">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10674">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_turkish_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10675">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10675">Keyword_turkish_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10676">TC Kim kim</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10676">TC Kimlik No</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10677">TC Kim numaras TC Kimmaras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10677">TC Kimlik numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10678">Vat vat vatandalLK numaras.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10678">Vatandaşlık numarası</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10679">Vatanda vat vatk no</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10679">Vatandaşlık no</span></span>

## <a name="uk-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10680">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10680">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10681">номер водительского удостоверения</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10681">driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10682">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации номера водительского удостоверения ЕС и доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10682">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10683">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10683">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10684">Сочетание 18 букв и цифр в указанном формате.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10684">Combination of 18 letters and digits in the specified format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10685">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10685">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10686">18 букв и цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10686">18 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10687">пять букв (без чувствительность к букве) или цифра "9" на месте буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10687">five letters (not case sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10688">одна цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10688">one digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10689">пять цифр в формате даты MMDDY для даты рождения (7-й знак приращен на 50, если драйвер — женщина, то есть от 51 до 62 вместо 01–12)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10689">five digits in the date format MMDDY for date of birth (7th character is incremented by 50 if driver is female, i.e. 51 to 62 instead of 01 to 12)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10690">две буквы (без чувствительность к букве) или цифра "9" в качестве буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10690">two letters (not case sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10691">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10691">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10692">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10692">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10693">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10693">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10694">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10694">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10695">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10695">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10696">функция Func_uk_drivers_license находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10696">The function Func_uk_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10697">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_drivers_license;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10697">A keyword from Keyword_uk_drivers_license is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10698">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10698">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="f93de4be-d94c-40df-a8be-461738047551" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10704">motor cars</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10704">motor cars</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10706">sidecar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10706">sidecar</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10707">трициклы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10707">tricycles</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10708">10</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10708">motorcycles</span></span>

## <a name="uk-electoral-roll-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10716">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10716">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10717">roll number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10717">electoral roll number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10718">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10718">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10719">две буквы, за которыми следуют 1–4 цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10719">two letters followed by 1-4 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10720">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10720">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10721">две буквы (без чувствительность к буквам), за которыми следуют 1–4 числа</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10721">two letters (not case sensitive) followed by 1-4 numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10722">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10722">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10723">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10723">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10724">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10724">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10725">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10725">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10726">регулярное выражение Regex_uk_electoral находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10726">The regular expression Regex_uk_electoral finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10727">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_electoral.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10727">A keyword from Keyword_uk_electoral is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Electoral Number -->
<Entity id="a3eea206-dc0c-4f06-9e22-aa1be3059963" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_uk_electoral" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_electoral" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10728">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10728">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_electoral"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10729">Keyword_uk_electoral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10729">Keyword_uk_electoral</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10731">nomination form</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10731">nomination form</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10732">electoral register</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10732">electoral register</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10733">electoral roll</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10733">electoral roll</span></span>

   
## <a name="uk-national-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10734">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10734">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10735">national health service number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10735">national health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10736">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10736">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10737">10–17 цифр, разделенных пробелами.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10737">10-17 digits separated by spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10738">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10738">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10739">10-17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10739">10-17 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10740">три или десять цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10740">either three or ten digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10741">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10741">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10742">три цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10742">three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10743">пробел</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10743">a space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10744">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10744">four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10745">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10745">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10746">Да</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10746">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10747">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10747">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10748">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10748">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10749">Функция Func_uk_nhs_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10749">The function Func_uk_nhs_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10750">Верно одно из условий ниже:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10750">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10751">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10751">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10752">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number1;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10752">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10753">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10753">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10754">Контрольная сумма проходит проверку.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10754">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. NHS Number -->
<Entity id="3192014e-2a16-44e9-aa69-4b20375c9a78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nhs_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10756">Keyword_uk_nhs_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10756">Keyword_uk_nhs_number</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10766">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10766">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10768">DOB</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10768">DOB</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10769">D.O.B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10769">D.O.B</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10770">Date of Birth</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10770">Date of Birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10771">Birth Date</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10771">Birth Date</span></span> 
   
## <a name="uk-national-insurance-number-nino"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10772">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10772">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10773">national insurance number (NINO)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10773">national insurance number (NINO)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10774">Этот объект типа конфиденциальной информации включается в тип конфиденциальной информации "National Identificaiton Number" в ЕС и доступен в качестве отдельного объекта типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10774">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identificaiton Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10775">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10775">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10776">семь или девять символов, разделенных пробелами или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10776">seven characters or nine characters separated by spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10777">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10777">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10778">два возможных шаблона:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10778">two possible patterns:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10779">две буквы (допустимые niNOs используют только определенные символы в этом префиксе, который проверяется этим шаблоном; без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10779">two letters (valid NINOs use only certain characters in this prefix, which this pattern validates; not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10780">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10780">six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10781">либо "A", "B", "C", либо "D" (как и префикс, в суффиксе разрешены только определенные символы, без чувствительность к буквам)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10781">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D' (like the prefix, only certain characters are allowed in the suffix; not case sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10782">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10782">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10783">две буквы</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10783">two letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10784">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10784">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10785">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10785">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10786">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10786">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10787">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10787">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10788">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10788">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10789">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10789">two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10790">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10790">a space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10791">"A", "B", "C" или "D"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10791">either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D'</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10792">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10792">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10793">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10793">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10794">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10794">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10795">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10795">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10796">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10796">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10797">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_uk_nino.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10797">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nino is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10798">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10798">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10799">функция Func_uk_nino находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10799">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.K. NINO -->
    <Entity id="16c07343-c26f-49d2-a987-3daf717e94cc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75" relaxProximity="true">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-unique-taxpayer-reference-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10821">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10821">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10822">Уникальный справочный номер налогоплательщика</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10822">Unique Taxpayer Reference Number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10823">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10823">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10824">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10824">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10825">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10825">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10826">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10826">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10827">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10827">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10828">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10828">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10829">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10829">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10830">10 цифр без пробелов и селитров</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10830">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
 
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10831">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10831">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10832">10 цифр.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10832">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10833">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10833">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10834">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10834">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10835">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10835">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10836">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10836">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10837">Функция находит  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10837">The function  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10838">Найдено ключевое  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` слово.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10838">A keyword from  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
      <!-- U.K. Unique Taxpayer Reference Number -->
      <Entity id="ad4a8116-0db8-439a-b545-6d967642f0ec" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

## <a name="us-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10858">Номер банковского счета в США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10858">U.S. bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10859">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10859">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10860">6–17 цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10860">6-17 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10861">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10861">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10862">6–17 последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10862">6-17 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10863">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10863">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10864">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10864">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10865">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10865">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10866">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10866">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10867">регулярное выражение Regex_usa_bank_account_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10867">The regular expression Regex_usa_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10868">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_usa_Bank_Account.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10868">A keyword from Keyword_usa_Bank_Account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.S. Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="a2ce32a8-f935-4bb6-8e96-2a5157672e2c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_usa_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_usa_Bank_Account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10898">Номер водительского удостоверения для США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10898">U.S. driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10899">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10899">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10900">Зависит от штата.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10900">Depends on the state</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10901">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10901">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10902">зависит от состояния, например Нью-Йорк:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10902">depends on the state -- for example, New York:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10903">будут совпадать девять цифр в формате ddd ddd ddd.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10903">nine digits formatted like ddd ddd ddd will match.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10904">девять цифр, например dddddd, не будут совпадать.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10904">nine digits like ddddddddd will not match.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10905">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10905">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10906">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10906">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10907">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10907">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10908">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10908">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10909">функция Func_new_york_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10909">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10910">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10910">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10911">обнаружено ключевое слово из списка Keyword_us_drivers_license.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10911">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10912">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10912">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10913">функция Func_new_york_drivers_license_number находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10913">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10914">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10914">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10915">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10915">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-10916">ни одно ключевое слово из Keyword_us_drivers_license не находится.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-10916">No keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="dfeb356f-61cd-459e-bf0f-7c6d28b458c6 patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-individual-taxpayer-identification-number-itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11014">Идентификационный номер налогоплательщика (ITIN) для США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11014">U.S. individual taxpayer identification number (ITIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11015">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11015">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11016">девять цифр, которые начинаются с "9" и содержат "7" или "8" в качестве четвертой цифры, при желании отформатированные с пробелами или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11016">nine digits that start with a "9" and contain a "7" or "8" as the fourth digit, optionally formatted with spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11017">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11017">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11018">отформатированный:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11018">formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11019">цифра "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11019">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11020">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11020">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11021">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11021">a space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11022">"7" или "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11022">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11023">цифра</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11023">a digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11024">пробел или тире</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11024">a space, or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11025">четыре цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11025">four digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11026">unformatted:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11026">unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11027">цифра "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11027">the digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11028">две цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11028">two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11029">"7" или "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11029">a "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11030">пять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11030">five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11031">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11031">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11032">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11032">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11033">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11033">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11034">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11034">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11035">Функция Func_formatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11035">The function Func_formatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11036">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_itin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11036">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11037">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11037">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11038">Функция Func_unformatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11038">The function Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11039">найдено ключевое слово из Keyword_itin;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11039">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11040">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11040">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11041">Функция Func_formatted_itin или Func_unformatted_itin находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11041">The function Func_formatted_itin or Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- U.S. Individual Taxpayer Identification Number (ITIN) -->
    <Entity id="e55e2a32-f92d-4985-a35d-a0b269eb687b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11042">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11042">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11043">Keyword_itin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11043">Keyword_itin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11044">налогоплательщик</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11044">taxpayer</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11046">tax identification</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11046">tax identification</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11047">itin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11047">itin</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11048">i.t.i.n.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11048">i.t.i.n.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11049">ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11049">ssn</span></span>

## <a name="us-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11056">Номер социального обеспечения (SSN) для США</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11056">U.S. social security number (SSN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11057">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11057">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11058">девять цифр, которые могут быть в форматированном или неформатированном шаблоне</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11058">nine digits, which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11059">Есть SSN выдан до середины 2011 г., он отличается строгим форматированием, при котором определенные части номера должны входить в указанные диапазоны (при этом нет контрольной суммы).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11059">If issued before mid-2011, an SSN has strong formatting where certain parts of the number must fall within certain ranges to be valid (but there's no checksum).</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11060">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11060">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11061">четыре функции искать SSNs в четырех различных шаблонах:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11061">four functions look for SSNs in four different patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11062">Func_ssn находит SSN со строгим форматированием с тире или пробелами, выданные до 2011 г. (ццц-цц-цццц ИЛИ ццц цц цццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11062">Func_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11063">Func_unformatted_ssn находит SSN со строгим форматированием, выданные до 2011 г. (без форматирования в виде девяти последовательных цифр — ццццццццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11063">Func_unformatted_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11064">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn находит SSN с тире или пробелами, выданные после 2011 г. (ццц-цц-цццц ИЛИ ццц цц цццц);</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11064">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11065">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn находит SSN без форматирования в виде девяти последовательных цифр, выданные после 2011 г. (ццццццццц).</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11065">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11066">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11066">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11067">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11067">No</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11068">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11068">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11069">Политика DLP имеет высокую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении с 300 символами:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11069">A DLP policy has high confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11070">Функция Func_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11070">The function Func_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11071">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11071">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11072">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11072">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11073">Функция Func_unformatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11073">The function Func_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11074">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11074">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11075">Политика DLP имеет низкую уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в расположении, в пределах 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11075">A DLP policy has low confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11076">Функция Func_randomized_formatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11076">The function Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11077">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11077">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11078">Политика защиты от потери данных с вероятностью в 55 % верно обнаружила этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в пределах ближайших 300 знаков:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11078">A DLP policy is 55% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11079">Функция Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11079">The function Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11080">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_ssn.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11080">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>


```xml
<!-- U.S. Social Security Number (SSN) -->
  <Entity id="a44669fe-0d48-453d-a9b1-2cc83f2cba77" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_formatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="55">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
  </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11081">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11081">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11082">Keyword_ssn</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11082">Keyword_ssn</span></span>

## <a name="us--uk-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11095">США и Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11095">U.S. / U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11096">passport number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11096">passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11097">Сша</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11097">The U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11098">Объект типа конфиденциальной информации passport number доступен в типе конфиденциальной информации номера паспорта ЕС и доступен как автономный объект типа конфиденциальной информации.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11098">passport number sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11099">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11099">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11100">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11100">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11101">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11101">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11102">девять последовательных цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11102">nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11103">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11103">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11104">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11104">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11105">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11105">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11106">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11106">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11107">функция Func_usa_uk_passport находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону;</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11107">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11108">находится ключевое слово из Keyword_passport.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11108">A keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="178ec42a-18b4-47cc-85c7-d62c92fd67f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11109">Ключевые слова</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11109">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11110">Keyword_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11110">Keyword_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11111">Passport Number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11111">Passport Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11112">Passport No</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11112">Passport No</span></span>

## <a name="ukraine-passport-domestic"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11129">Внутренний паспорт гражданина Украины</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11129">Ukraine passport domestic</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11130">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11130">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11131">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11131">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11132">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11132">communication compliance policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11133">управление информацией</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11133">information governance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11134">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11134">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11135">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11135">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11136">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11136">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11137">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11137">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11138">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11138">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11139">девять цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11139">nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11140">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11140">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11141">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11141">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11142">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11142">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11143">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11143">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11144">Regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11144">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11145">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11145">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport Domestic -->
      <Entity id="1817a540-221f-4459-9202-3bd78b81d803" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_Domestic"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11155">Этот тип конфиденциальной информации доступен только в:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11155">This sensitive information type is only available for use in:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11156">политики защиты от потери данных</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11156">data loss prevention policies</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11157">политики соответствия коммуникациям</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11157">communication compliance policies</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11159">управление записями</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11159">records management</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11160">Безопасность облачных приложений Майкрософт</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11160">Microsoft cloud app security</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11161">Format</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11161">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11162">восьми-символьный буквонумерный шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11162">eight-character alphanumeric pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11163">Шаблон</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11163">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11164">восьми-символьный буквонумерный шаблон:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11164">eight-character alphanumeric pattern:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11165">две буквы или цифры</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11165">two letters or digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11166">шесть цифр</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11166">six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11167">Контрольная сумма</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11167">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11168">Нет</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11168">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11169">Определение</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11169">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11170">Политика DLP имеет среднюю уверенность в том, что она обнаруживает этот тип конфиденциальной информации, если в близости от 300 символов:</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11170">A DLP policy has medium confidence that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11171">Regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International находит содержимое, которое соответствует шаблону.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11171">The regex Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="8a85c-11172">Находится ключевое слово из Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="8a85c-11172">A keyword from Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- Ukraine Passport International -->
      <Entity id="cfbe032d-22e0-4f28-ab68-d66e9641f1e2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Ukraine_Passport_International"/>
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```
